%20of%20America%20at%20a%2074%25%20premium%2C%20Loudon%20made%20a%20%241.76%20million%20profit.%20His%20wife%2C%20then%20a%20BP%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions%20manager%20who%20was%20working%20on%20the%20deal%2C%20was%20unaware%20of%20his%20trading%2C%20the%20regulator%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20lawsuits%20from%20the%20SEC%20and%20US%20prosecutors%20in%20Texas%2C%20Tyler%20got%20the%20idea%20to%20buy%20TravelCenters%20after%20learning%20of%20the%20potential%20deal%20from%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20was%20working%20on%20the%20deal%20in%20a%20home%20office%2020%20feet%20away.%20When%20he%20ultimately%20confessed%20to%20her%2C%20she%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20house%20and%20later%20filed%20for%20divorce.%20She%20reported%20his%20trades%20to%20BP%2C%20who%20then%20fired%20her%20despite%20finding%20no%20evidence%20that%20she%20knowingly%20leaked%20the%20deal%2C%20according%20to%20the%20SEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20settlement%2C%20Loudon%20agreed%20to%20give%20up%20the%20money%20he%20made%20on%20the%20transactions%20and%20pay%20a%20fine.%20Loudon's%20lawyer%2C%20Peter%20Zeidenberg%2C%20didn't%20immediately%20reply%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20BP%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20to%20buy%20TravelCenters%20of%20America%20Inc.%20for%20about%20%241.3%20billion%20gave%20the%20British%20oil%20major%20access%20to%20a%20network%20of%20US%20gas%20stations.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20transaction%2C%20TravelCenters%20had%20a%20network%20of%20281%20locations%20in%2044%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20work-from-home%20era%20began%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%20SEC%20has%20brought%20multiple%20insider-trading%20cases%20involving%20information%20overheard%20or%20seen%20while%20working%20from%20home%20with%20a%20significant%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20SEC%2C%20Loudon's%20eavesdropping%20extended%20abroad.%20While%20traveling%20in%20Rome%2C%20the%20SEC%20said%20Loudon%20sat%20nearby%20his%20wife%20while%20she%20worked%20on%20the%20TravelCenters%20deal%20from%20a%20small%20rented%20apartment.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708664220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fh5cef0kg_work-from-home_625x300_23_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-eavesdropped-on-wifes-calls-during-wfh-gets-insider-trading-charge-5111008%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Texas%20man%20made%20almost%20%242%20million%20by%20illegally%20trading%20on%20his%20wife's%20conversations%20with%20her%20BP%20Plc%20colleagues%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20in%20its%20latest%20case%20about%20couples%20eavesdropping%20while%20working%20from%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-eavesdropped-on-wifes-calls-during-wfh-gets-insider-trading-charge-5111008%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-eavesdropped-on-wifes-calls-during-wfh-gets-insider-trading-charge-5111008%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-eavesdropped-on-wifes-calls-during-wfh-gets-insider-trading-charge-5111008%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224th%20Test%20Day%201%20Live%3A%20Akash%20Removes%20Duckett%20On%20Debut%2C%20ENG%201%20Down%20vs%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20vs%20England%204th%20Test%20Day%201%20Live%20Updates%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Debutant%20Akash%20Deep%20has%20provided%20India%20with%20two%20big%20breakthroughs.%20He%20dismissed%20Ben%20Duckett%20and%20Ollie%20Pope%20in%20the%20same%20over%20as%20England%20lose%20two%20wickets%