bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68377379%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68377379.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68377379.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi's%20One-Hour%20Phone%20Call%20With%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20Amid%20Seats%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Congress%20labours%20through%20intense%20seat%20negotiations%20with%20INDIA%20bloc%20allies%20ahead%20of%20the%20national%20election%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20dialled%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20yesterday%20to%20discuss%20the%20deadlock%20over%20eight%20of%20Maharashtra's%2048%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20reportedly%20spoke%20to%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20for%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20say%20sources%2C%20want%20to%20contest%20three%20of%20Mumbai's%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20-%20Mumbai%20South%20Central%2C%20Mumbai%20North%20Central%20and%20Mumbai%20North%20West.%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20reportedly%20wants%20to%20contest%2018%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20four%20in%20Mumbai%20-%20Mumbai%20South%2C%20Mumbai%20North%20West%2C%20Mumbai%20North%20East%20and%20Mumbai%20South%20Central.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20alliance%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20seat%20talks%20are%20entirely%20uncharted%20territory%20as%20the%20parties%20formed%20the%20ideologically%20mismatched%20alliance%20after%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%202019.%20The%20three%20have%20managed%20an%20agreement%20on%20nearly%2040%20seats%20but%20negotiators%20are%20stuck%20on%20eight%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%20fought%2022%20of%2048%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20won%2018%2C%20including%20three%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUddhav%20Thackeray's%20party%20ended%20its%2025-year%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20months%20later%2C%20after%20failing%20to%20agree%20on%20power-sharing%20terms%20following%20the%20Maharashtra%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20government%20collapsed%20after%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20split%20and%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20faction%20formed%20a%20new%20government%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20suffered%20a%20similar%20rupture%2C%20with%20the%20veteran's%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%20joining%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-BJP%20coalition%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20fears%20a%20similar%20exodus%20after%20two%20of%20its%20prominent%20leaders%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%2C%20and%20Milind%20Deora%2C%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defections%20have%20complicated%20the%20seat%20negotiations%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20opposition%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20party%2C%20after%20the%20Congress%20defections%2C%20wants%20a%20greater%20share%20in%20Mumbai%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20sources%20assert%20that%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20are%20all%20determined%20to%20make%20it%20work%2C%20aware%20that%20for%20each%20party%2C%20it%20is%20a%20battle%20for%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20recently%20sealed%20difficult%20seat%20sharing%20deals%20with%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Samajwadi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20redoubled%20efforts%20to%20close%20a%20deal%20with%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20has%20refused%20to%20part%20with%20more%20than%20five%20of%20her%20state's%2042%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708663140000