20show's%20first%20season%2C%20%26quot%3BTrue%20Detective%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20anthology%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20nature%20would%20suggest%20that%20we%20won't%20be%20seeing%20%26quot%3BNight%20Country%26quot%3B%20part%20two%20and%20that%20season%20five%20will%20feature%20an%20entirely%20new%20story.%20You%20probably%20shouldn't%20bet%20on%20seeing%20anything%20else%20out%20of%20Ennis%2C%20Alaska.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EL%C3%B3pez%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Ftv%2Ftv-features%2Ftrue-detective-night-country-issa-lopez-nic-pizzolatto-franchise-future-1235831392%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hollywood%20Reporter%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20her%20cast%20was%20lobbying%20her%20to%20consider%20returning%20to%20%26quot%3BNight%20Country%26quot%3B%20for%20another%20season.%20While%20she%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%26quot%3B%20to%20hear%20that%20her%20cast%20wanted%20to%20return%20to%20their%20characters%2C%20she%20ultimately%20thought%20that%20it%20would%20be%20doing%20them%20a%20disservice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20tempting%2C%26quot%3B%20L%C3%B3pez%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20do%20feel%20that%20the%20characters%20grew.%20It's%20a%20lot%20more%20boring%20to%20do%20drama%20about%20grown%20people%20than%20people%20that%20need%20growth.%20So%20I%20don't%20think%20I'll%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHBO%20and%20L%C3%B3pez%20haven't%20announced%20any%20further%20details%20about%20the%20plot%20of%20the%20new%20season%20%E2%80%94%20so%20stay%20tuned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWho's%20in%20the%20cast%20of%20'True%20Detective'%20season%205%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20it's%20a%20toss-up.%20We%20don't%20have%20any%20details%20on%20the%20cast%20at%20this%20point%20in%20time%2C%20but%20you%20can%20probably%20expect%20a%20batch%20of%20fresh%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20will%20'True%20Detective'%20season%205%20come%20out%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20the%20show%20was