2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20World%20Trade%20Organization's%20Upcoming%20MC13%20Conference%20Is%20Significant%20for%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22174008%2FEffect-2024-02-22T173917.998.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20less%20than%20a%20week%20to%20go%20until%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%E2%80%99s%2013th%20Ministerial%20Conference%20(MC13)%2C%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20from%20February%2026%2C%20consensus%20from%20all%20members%20on%20support%20for%20the%20proposed%C2%A0Investment%C2%A0Facilitation%C2%A0for%C2%A0Development%C2%A0Agreement%C2%A0(IFDA)%20is%20still%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20IFDA%20has%20thus%20far%20received%20the%20support%20of%20three-quarters%20of%20WTO%20members%2C%20while%20some%20prominent%20members%2C%20such%20as%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20have%20opposed%20this%20initiative%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20lacking%20a%20formal%20mandate%20and%20may%20not%20give%20their%20consent%20to%20the%20proposed%20IFDA%20at%20MC13.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20supporting%20countries%2C%20led%20by%20China%2C%20seek%20to%20incorporate%20the%20proposed%C2%A0agreement%C2%A0into%20the%20WTO%20rulebook%20as%20a%20standalone%20plurilateral%C2%A0agreement%C2%A0under%20Annex%204.%20However%2C%20the%20process%20of%20integrating%20the%20proposed%20IFDA%20into%20the%20WTO%20rulebook%20requires%20a%20decision%20to%20be%20adopted%20by%20consensus%20among%20all%20WTO%20members%2C%20even%20though%20some%20members%20may%20not%20join%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20IFDA%20receives%20support%20from%20all%20members%20at%20MC13%2C%20it%20will%20be%20the%20first%20plurilateral%C2%A0agreement%C2%A0since%20the%20founding%20of%20the%20WTO.%20If%20this%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20the%20IFDA%20would%20potentially%20open%20the%20door%20to%20more%20plurilateral%20agreements%20on%20new%20issues%20and%20regional%20specifics%20while%20rendering%20the%20institutional%20foundations%20of%20the%20multilateral%20trading%20system%20more%20fragile.%20In%20effect%2C%20this%20would%20drastically%20alter%20the%20character%20of%20the%20WTO%2C%20which%20is%20the%20core%20of%20the%20multilateral%20trading%20system.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20decision%20on%20the%20IFDA%20at%20MC13%20would%20have%20much%20wider%20ramifications%20for%20the%20future%20of%20the%20multilateral%20trading%20system%20than%20are%20currently%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20subset%20of%C2%A0investment%C2%A0issues%2C%C2%A0investment%C2%A0facilitation%C2%A0refers%20to%20simplifying%20administrative%20procedures%2C%20improving%20transparency%2C%20and%20enhancing%20relations%20with%20stakeholders%20so%20that%20it%20becomes%20easier%20for%20investors%20to%20establish%2C%20operate%20and%20exit%20investments.%20Some%20of%20the%20controversial%20issues%20related%20to%20market%20access%2C%C2%A0investment%C2%A0protection%20and%20investor-state%20dispute%20settlement%20are%20not%20included%20in%20the%20proposed%20IFDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImplementation%20Hurdles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20IFDA%20becomes%20a%20reality%2C%20the%20hard%20part%20will%20begin%20with%20its%20implementation.%20Large%20and%20diverse%20countries%20with%20federal%20and%20decentralised%20forms%20of%20government%20will%20find%20it%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20implement%20some%20of%20the%20key%20provisions%20of%20the%20proposed%C2%A0agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22174245%2FEffect-2024-02-22T174216.655.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22174245%2FEffect-2024-02-22T174216.655.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22174245%2FEffect-2024-02-22T174216.655-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22174245%2FEffect-2024-02-22T174216.655-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20previous%20edition%20(12th%20edition)%20of%20Ministerial%20Conference%20of%20World%20Trade%20Organization%20held%20in%20Geneva%20in%202022.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20via%20video%20on%20WTO%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20coordinators%20of%20the%20IFDA%20negotiations%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20make%20public%20the%20agreed%20text%20(of%20July%206)%20before%20MC13%2C%20a%20cursory%20look%20at%20this%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilaterals.org%2F%3Fwto-investment-facilitation-for%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilaterals.org%2F%3Fwto-investment-facilitation-for%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708686463985000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3YQgoLQ-KL82DpcBvQpNgU%5C%22%3Eleaked%20text%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%20many%20provisions%20may%20be%20easier%20to%20implement%20in%20small%20countries%20and%20city-states%20(such%20as%20Singapore%20and%20Monaco)%20than%20in%20a%20country%20as%20large%20and%20diverse%20as%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20consider%20the%20case%20of%20a%20member%E2%80%99s%20obligations%20under%20the%20proposed%20IFDA.%20Article%202.3%20of%20the%20leaked%20text%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20Member%E2%80%99s%2FParty%E2%80%99s%20obligations%20under%20this%C2%A0Agreement%C2%A0shall%20apply%20to%20measures%20adopted%20or%20maintained%20by%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(a)%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0its%20central%2C%20regional%20or%20local%20governments%20and%20authorities%3B%20and%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(b)%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0non-governmental%20bodies%20in%20the%20exercise%20of%20powers%20delegated%20by%20central%2C%20regional%20or%20local%20governments%20or%20authorities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Article%202.4%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20fulfilling%20its%20obligations%20and%20commitments%20under%20this%C2%A0Agreement%2C%20each%20Member%2FParty%20shall%20take%20such%20reasonable%20measures%20as%20may%20be%20available%20to%20it%20to%20ensure%20their%20observance%20by%20regional%20and%20local%20governments%20and%20authorities%20and%20non-governmental%20bodies%20within%20its%20territory.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20author%20is%20well-acquainted%20with%20the%20Indian%20administrative%20system%2C%20let%20us%20attempt%20to%20place%20the%20above%20provisions%20in%20the%20Indian%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20state%20governments%2C%20and%20local%20bodies%20(e.g.%2C%20municipalities%20and%20municipal%20councils)%20have%20jurisdiction%20over%20different%20investment%20issues.%20An%20investor%20(domestic%20or%20foreign)%20must%20approach%20different%20Indian%20authorities%20%E2%80%93%20for%20land%20acquisition%2C%20building%20permits%20and%20pollution%20certificates%20(mainly%20municipalities%20and%20local%20authorities%2C%20but%20varies%20across%20states)%3B%20compliance%20with%20environmental%20regulations%20(Ministry%20of%20Environment)%3B%20license%20from%20sectoral%20regulators%20(e.g.%2C%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India)%20%E2%80%93%20depending%20on%20the%20type%20of%20business.%20As%20land%20is%20principally%20a%20state%20subject%20under%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20New%20Delhi%20cannot%20decide%20on%20transparency%20or%20administrative%20procedures%20related%20to%20land%20issues.%20This%20issue%20falls%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%2037%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%203%2C700%20local%20authorities%20in%20India%20(comprising%20100%20municipalities%2C%202100%20nagar%20panchayats%2C%20and%201500%20municipal%20councils)%20that%20issue%20building%20permits%20and%20pollution%20certificates%20for%20setting%20up%20factories%20and%20offices.%20Investment%20facilitation%20measures%20such%20as%20transparency%20norms%20and%20administrative%20procedures%20fall%20within%20the%20remit%20of%20these%20local%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20India%E2%80%99s%20peculiar%20administrative%20system%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20imagine%20whether%20all%20local%20bodies%20and%20state%20governments%20will%20cooperate%20with%20the%20central%20government%20to%20implement%20a%20legally%20binding%20IFDA%20if%20India%20decides%20to%20join%20the%20proposed%20agreement.%20Given%20these%20circumstances%2C%20New%20Delhi%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20ensure%20full%20compliance%20with%20the%20IFDA%20commitments%20in%20a%20time-bound%20manner%20by%20different%20state%20governments%20and%20local%20authorities.%20It%20is%20worth%20remembering%20that%20it%20took%2017%20years%20of%20consensus%20building%20to%20roll%20out%20a%20nationwide%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20a%20single%20information%20portal%20(Article%208)%20and%20focal%20point%20(Article%2022)%20would%20be%20ineffective%20in%20India%20because%20of%20its%20peculiar%20administrative%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20India%20or%20any%20other%20member%20country%20will%20alter%20its%20administrative%20system%20to%20meet%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20proposed%20IFDA%2C%20whose%20purported%20gains%20are%20intangible%2C%20while%20the%20burden%20of%20implementing%20demanding%20provisions%20is%20heavy.%20This%20burden%20cannot%20be%20alleviated%20through%20technical%20assistance%20and%20capacity-building%20measures%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%20July%206%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESustainable%C2%A0Investment%3A%20No%20Teeth%20That%20Bite%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20July%206%20text%20devotes%20an%20entire%20section%20to%20sustainable%20investment%20and%20includes%20two%20provisions%20on%20%E2%80%9Cresponsible%20business%20conduct%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmeasures%20against%20corruption%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20the%20expectation%20that%20these%20measures%20would%20facilitate%20higher-quality%20investments%20and%20thereby%20promote%20sustainable%20development%20in%20host%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20analysts%20may%20view%20the%20inclusion%20of%20these%20provisions%20as%20a%20major%20departure%20from%20previous%20WTO%20agreements%2C%20but%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20these%20provisions%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20exempted%20from%20dispute%20settlement%20proceedings.%20Article%2044.4%20of%20the%20text%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CMembers%2FParties%20shall%20not%20have%20recourse%20to%20dispute%20settlement%20under%20this%20Article%20for%20matters%20arising%20under%20Article%2037%20on%20%E2%80%9CResponsible%20business%20conduct%E2%80%9D%20and%20Article%2038%20on%20%E2%80%9CMeasures%20against%20corruption%E2%80%9D.%E2%80%9D%20In%20other%20words%2C%20no%20dispute%20claims%20can%20be%20raised%20against%20the%20non-implementation%20of%20these%20two%20provisions%20on%20sustainable%C2%A0investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20there%20are%20no%20binding%20obligations%20for%20private%20investors%20and%20home%20countries%20to%20encourage%20responsible%20business%20conduct%20in%20the%20July%206%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20bigger%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%20practical%20considerations%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20question%20of%20policy%20space.%20There%20is%20a%20legitimate%20concern%20that%20legally%20binding%20commitments%20on%20investment%20facilitation%20and%20their%20enforcement%20under%20the%20WTO%20will%20restrict%20the%20policy%20space%20for%20member%20countries%20to%20choose%20the%20best%20mix%20of%20policies%20and%20instruments%20that%20are%20consistent%20with%20their%20peculiar%20administrative%20structures%20and%20local%20conditions.%20A%20bottom-up%20approach%20is%20more%20effective%20and%20appropriate%20for%20countries%20to%20design%20investment%20facilitation%20measures%20that%20take%20local%20circumstances%20into%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20should%20countries%20opt%20for%20a%20top-down%2C%20legally%20binding%20plurilateral%C2%A0agreement%C2%A0when%20more%20flexible%20and%20beneficial%20options%20for%C2%A0investment%C2%A0facilitation%C2%A0are%20available%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20option%20is%20to%20pursue%20a%20unilateral%20approach%20to%C2%A0investment%C2%A0facilitation%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20being%20adopted%20by%20all%20WTO%20members.%20Members%20have%20been%2C%20and%20are%2C%20unilaterally%20implementing%20a%20wide%20range%20of%C2%A0investment%C2%A0facilitation%C2%A0measures%20at%20the%20national%20and%20subnational%20levels%2C%20as%20per%20their%20administrative%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20option%20is%20to%20pursue%C2%A0investment%C2%A0facilitation%C2%A0measures%20through%20voluntary%20non-binding%20mechanisms.%20Some%20of%20these%20recent%20initiatives%20include%3A%20UNCTAD%E2%80%99s%20Global%20Action%20Menu%20for%C2%A0Investment%C2%A0Facilitation%C2%A0(2017)%2C%20Outlines%20for%20BRICS%C2%A0Investment%C2%A0Facilitation%C2%A0(2017)%2C%20and%20the%20EU-India%C2%A0Investment%C2%A0Facilitation%C2%A0Mechanism%20(2017).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20option%20to%20promote%C2%A0investment%C2%A0facilitation%C2%A0is%20through%20policy%20advice%2C%20technical%20assistance%2C%20and%20capacity%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20conclude%2C%C2%A0investment%C2%A0facilitation%C2%A0is%20just%20one%20instrument%20that%20attracts%C2%A0investment%2C%20and%20it%20is%20by%20far%20not%20as%20important%20as%20a%20country%E2%80%99s%20economic%20determinants.%20Many%20states%20in%20India%20(such%20as%20Punjab%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh)%20have%20established%20single-window%20systems%20and%20streamlined%20administrative%20procedures%20with%20time-bound%20approvals%20of%C2%A0investment%C2%A0proposals%3B%20however%2C%20such%20measures%20have%20not%20always%20been%20accompanied%20by%20increased%20investments%20(domestic%20or%20foreign).%20The%20same%20has%20been%20the%20case%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20calling%20into%20question%20the%20efficacy%20of%C2%A0investment%C2%A0facilitation%C2%A0measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20close%20to%20120%20members%20backing%20the%20proposed%20IFDA%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20members%20will%20give%20it%20a%20green%20signal%20at%20MC13%2C%20given%20the%20centrality%20of%20%E2%80%9Cconsensus-based%20decision%C2%A0making%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20WTO%2C%20as%20emphasised%20in%20the%20Marrakesh%C2%A0Agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20week%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20MC13.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKavaljit%20Singh%20works%20with%20Madhyam%2C%20New%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708655381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22174008%2FEffect-2024-02-22T173917.998.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhy-world-trade-organizations-upcoming-mc13-conference-is-significant-for-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2013th%20Ministerial%20Conference%20starting%20on%20February%2026%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20will%20see%20discussion%20on%20the%20proposed%20Investment%C2%A0Facilitation%C2%A0for%C2%A0Development%C2%A0Agreement%20which%20India%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20other%20prominent%20members%20opposed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhy-world-trade-organizations-upcoming-mc13-conference-is-significant-for-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Was%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20Rested%20For%20Ra