%20shareholder%20agreements%20by%20calling%20for%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EProbe%20Agency%20Notice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20Mr%20Raveendran's%20problems%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20yesterday%20upgraded%20its%20Look%20Out%20Circular%20(LC)%20against%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act%20(FEMA)%20probe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Look%20Out%20Circular%2C%20initially%20issued%20over%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20has%20undergone%20recent%20modifications%20to%20address%20investor%20apprehensions%20and%20the%20evolving%20nature%20of%20the%20FEMA%20probe.%20The%20ED%20has%20requested%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Immigration%20to%20enhance%20the%20circular%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20Mr%20Raveendran%20does%20not%20leave%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency's%20move%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20substantial%20foreign%20exchange%20violation%20show%20cause%20notice%2C%20exceeding%20Rs%209%2C300%20crore%2C%20issued%20against%20Byju's%20and%20Mr%20Raveendran%20in%20November%20last%20year.%20The%20probe%20agency%20cited%20multiple%20grounds%20for%20the%20charges%2C%20including%20the%20alleged%20failure%20to%20submit%20import%20documents%20against%20advance%20remittances%20made%20outside%20India%20and%20delays%20in%20filing%20documents%20related%20to%20exports%20made%20outside%20India%20against%20the%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investment%20(FDI)%20received%20by%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20a%20foreign%20unit%20of%20Byju's%2C%20based%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Delaware%2C%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%2C%20%C2%A0listing%20liabilities%20in%20the%20range%20of%20%241%20billion%20to%20%2410%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Downfall%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20started%20its%20venture%20in%202006%20by%20offering%20classes%20for%20MBA%20aspirants%20preparing%20for%20the%20CAT%20exam.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20edtech%20firm%20diversified%20its%20offerings%2C%20extending%20its%20reach%20from%20postgraduate%20to%20undergraduate%20and%20eventually%20school%20students.%20In%202015%2C%20it%20launched%20Byju's%20learning%20app%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20company%20to%20become%20India's%20first%20ed-tech%20unicorn%20in%20just%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Covid%20pandemic%20became%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20Byju's%20as%20schools%20closed%20their%20doors%2C%20and%20education%20transitioned%20swiftly%20to%20online%20platforms.%20Byju's%20seized%20the%20moment%2C%20launched%20an%20extensive%20marketing%20campaign%2C%20and%20hired%20thousands%20to%20meet%20the%20demands%20of%20online%20education%20during%20the%20pandemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20secured%20sponsorship%20deals%20with%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%2C%20and%20even%20roped%20in%20football%20maestro%20Lionel%20Messi%20as%20a%20global%20ambassador.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20allegations%20of%20a%20toxic%20work%20atmosphere%20and%20aggressive%20marketing%20practices%20that%20allegedly%20harassed%20parents%20began%20to%20surface.%20Prosus%2C%20a%20major%20shareholder%2C%20slashed%20Byju's%20valuation%20by%20a%20staggering%2075%20per%20cent%2C%20triggering%20a%20cascade%20of%20events.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMass%20layoffs%20ensued%20culminating%20in%20the%20company%20losing%20billions%20and%20getting%20entangled%20in%20a%20series%20of%20legal%20troubles.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708653480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fmh11kjs8_byju-raveendran-afp-650_625x300_01_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Ffate-of-byjus-billionaire-founder-byju-raveendran-hinges-on-big-investors-meet-today-5110386%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fate%20of%20Byju%20Raveendran%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20ed-tech%20giant%20Byju's%2C%20hangs%20in%20the%20balance%20as%20an%20ex