0expensive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELanding%20on%20the%20moon%20is%20no%20easy%20feat.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-moon-lander-peregrine-burn-up-earth-atmosphere-satellite-astrobotic-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20isn't%20the%20only%20nation%20to%20have%20tried%20and%20failed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20previous%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20only%20found%20success%20several%20years%20after%20crashing%20during%20its%20first%20attempt.%20Russia's%20lunar%20lander%20was%20destroyed%20in%20a%20crash%20in%20August%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-moon-probe-landed-upside-down-still-works-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapan's%20landed%20upside%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221260%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20IM-1%20mission%20spacecraft%20floating%20in%20space%20with%20Earth%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d65e9ea3bd891424f90c71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22945%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIntuitive%20Machines%20captured%20this%20image%20of%20the%20Odysseus%20moon%20lander%20as%20it%20flew%20away%20from%20Earth.%3Cp%3EIntuitive%20Machines%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpaceflight%20is%20hard.%20A%20million%20things%20have%20to%20go%20right%2C%20and%20if%20one%20thing%20goes%20wrong%2C%20you%20can%20still%20have%20a%20failure%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vice%20President%20of%20Intuitive%20Machines's%20space%20systems%2C%20Trent%20Martin%2C%20during%20a%20NASA%20press%20briefing%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20only%20about%2050%25%20of%20lunar%20landing%20missions%20succeed.%20While%20technology%20has%20advanced%20a%20lot%20since%20Apollo%2C%20the%20moon's%20treacherous%20terrain%20and%20distance%20from%20Earth%20make%20failure%20pretty%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESpace%20exploration%20goes%20commercial%3C%2Fh2%3E%3C