%20Commission%20also%20said%20it's%20investigating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20reported%20wireless%20outages%2C%20and%20our%20Public%20Safety%20and%20Homeland%20Security%20Bureau%20is%20actively%20investigating%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20shared%20in%20a%20statement%20with%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20AT%26amp%3BT%20and%20public%20safety%20authorities%2C%20including%20FirstNet%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20providers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20also%20confirmed%20that%20they%20are%20looking%20into%20the%20outage%20and%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bshould%20we%20learn%20of%20any%20malicious%20activity%20we%20will%20respond%20accordingly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKirby%20said%20that%20US%20officials%20have%20been%20told%20that%20AT%26amp%3BT%20had%20no%20reason%20to%20think%20the%20outage%20was%20a%20cyber%20security%20incident%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20inconveniencing%20customers%2C%20the%20issue%20threatened%20emergency%20services%20nationwide%20since%20people%20couldn't%20make%20phone%20calls%20or%20send%20text%20messages.%20Local%20officials%20and%20emergency%20departments%20pushed%20out%20alerts%20throughout%20the%20day%20advising%20people%20to%20use%20Wi-Fi%20to%20make%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20network%20was%20taking%20steps%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20issue%20doesn't%20happen%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFebruary%2022%2C%202024%3A%20This%20story%20has%20been%20updated%20to%20include%20AT%26amp%3BT's%20update%20about%20the%20outage.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-homeland-security-investigating-att-cell-phone-outage-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708640405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%2