anada-68374795%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Day%20After%20Farmer's%20Death%2C%20SKM%20Announces%20Wider%20Programmes%3B%20Nationwide%20Protest%20Set%20for%20Friday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0A%20day%20after%20the%20death%20of%20a%20farmer%20amid%20excessive%20police%20action%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20suspended%20the%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20protesting%20farmers%2C%20signalling%20its%20continuous%20efforts%20to%20suppress%20the%20latest%20edition%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%2C%20currently%20stalled%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20unity%20among%20farmer%20organisations%20is%20far%20from%20evident%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%2C%20an%20umbrella%20organisation%20of%20farmer%20unions%20across%20the%20country%20that%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20compelling%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20repeal%20three%20farm%20laws%20during%20their%20year-long%20protest%20in%202020%2C%20decided%20not%20to%20join%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20barriers%20during%20their%20general%20body%20meeting%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Thursday%2C%20February%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20it%20announced%20its%20own%20parallel%20programmes%2C%20from%20holding%20a%20day-long%20%E2%80%98kisan%20mahapanchayat%E2%80%99%20in%20Delhi%20next%20month%20on%20March%2014%20to%20organising%20a%20tractor%20march%20on%20highways%20later%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20%E2%80%9CDelhi%20Chalo%E2%80%9D%20programme%20is%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20SKM%20splinter%20group%2C%20SKM%20(non-political)%2C%20under%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20and%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangarsh%20Committee%20under%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20why%20the%20SKM%20decided%20not%20to%20join%20the%20protesting%20farmers%2C%20Balbir%20Singh%20Rajewal%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20SKM%2C%20told%20the%20media%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20these%20groups%20decided%20to%20march%20for%20Delhi%20without%20consulting%20the%20SKM.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20join%20them%20now%2C%20it%20would%20give%20the%20impression%20that%20we%20are%20going%20there%20to%20disturb%20their%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajewal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20SKM%20was%20not%20showing%20unity%2C%20Rajewal%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20media%20should%20not%20put%20their%20words%20on%20our%20mouth.%20Our%20focus%20is%20on%20unity%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%20all%20farmers.%20Despite%20the%20separation%20of%20the%20Dallewal%20and%20Pandher%20groups%20from%20the%20SKM%2C%20we%20have%20still%20formed%20a%20six-member%20committee%20to%20establish%20coordination%20with%20them%20and%20advance%20our%20common%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajewal%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20on%20whether%20protesting%20farmers%20should%20march%20ahead%20or%20call%20off%20their%20protest%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20strong%20police%20action%20is%20for%20them%20to%20make%2C%20as%20they%20are%20managing%20the%20entire%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%E2%80%99s%20decision%20came%20a%20day%20after%20Dallewal%20invited%20all%20farm%20unions%20to%20bolster%20their%20protest%20at%20the%20borders%2C%20following%20the%20death%20of%20a%20farmer%20at%20the%20Khanauri%20border%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20calm%20at%20the%20borders%20since%20their%20Delhi%20march%20remains%20suspended%20till%20Friday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandher%20told%20the%20media%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Thursday%20that%20they%20would%20announce%20their%20next%20course%20of%20action%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESKM%20anno