20slopes%20of%20the%20north%20Kashmir%20ski%20resort%2C%20a%20rescue%20team%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20area%20and%20helicopters%20were%20also%20deployed%20to%20help%20in%20the%20search%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20collaborative%20effort%20between%20the%20Gulmarg%20Ski%20Patrol%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20and%20other%20state%20agencies%20resulted%20in%20the%20successful%20rescue%20of%20the%20group%20as%20well%20as%20one%20local%20guide%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slain%20skier%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Hanten%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Moscow.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20body%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20the%20Tangmarg%20sub-district%20hospital%20for%20post-mortem%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20quoted%20a%20local%20police%20officer%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Embassy%20of%20Russia%20in%20India%20maintains%20constant%20contact%20with%20the%20local%20authorities.%20The%20avalanche%20was%20triggered%20by%20the%20heavy%20snowfall%20observed%20in%20the%20region%20since%20February%2017.%20On%20February%2021%2C%20a%20medium%20danger%20level%20avalanche%20warning%20was%20issued%20for%20Baramulla%20district%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20Russian%20embassy%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20from%20the%20scene%20of%20a%20slope%20on%20Mt%20Afarwat%2C%20which%20was%20hit%20by%20the%20avalanche%2C%20showed%20a%20private%20chopper%20landing%20near%20tall%20mounds%20of%20snow.%20The%20local%20guide%20remained%20missing%20for%20some%20time%20but%20he%20was%20rescued%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20edition%20of%20Khelo%20India%20Games%20or%20National%20Winter%20Games%2C%20which%20were%20inaugurated%C2%A0%20in%20Gulmarg%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20were%20not%20affected%20by%20the%20avalanche%2C%20officials%20said.%20The%20games%20are%20expected%20to%20continue%20till%20February%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20was%20also%20in%20Gulmarg%20when%20the%20tragedy%20happened%20and%20he%20posted%20about%20the%20incident%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20appears%20the%20skiers%20were%20skiing%20off%20the%20piste%20or%20groomed%20slopes%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98back%20country%E2%80%99.%20Days%20like%20today%20remind%20us%20that%20while%20the%20skiing%20is%20fun%2C%20the%20fresh%20powder%20exhilarating%20%26amp%3B%20the%20visuals%20spectacular%2C%20skiing%20is%20not%20without%20its%20dangers%20%26amp%3B%20risk%20to%20lives.%20Praying%20that%20all%20the%20missing%20skiers%20are%20found%20alive%20%26amp%3B%20the%20reports%20of%20a%20casualty%20end%20up%20being%20unfounded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECricketing%20legend%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20who%20is%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20was%20also%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Gulmarg%20which%20has%20recorded%20a%20bumper%20snowfall%20this%20week%20after%20a%20prolonged%20spell%20of%20dry%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snow%20has%20brought%20cheer%20for%20the%20hotel%20industry%20and%20other%20local%20stakeholders.%20After%20the%20bumper%20snowfall%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20there%20have%20been%20frequent%20traffic%20jams%20on%20Gulmarg-Tangmarg%20road%20due%20to%20the%20heavy%20influx%20of%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNearly%20all%20the%20hotels%20in%20Gulmarg%20are%20full%20and%20we%20are%20expecting%20the%20trend%20to%20continue%20for%20another%20two-three%20weeks%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20tourism%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20heavy%20snowfall%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20Kashmir%20this%20week%2C%20officials%20have%20been%20issuing%20avalanche%20warnings%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20A%20massive%20avalanche%20struck%20Sonamarg%20health%20resort%20in%20central%20Kashmir%20earlier%20this%20month%20but%20there%20were%20no%20fatalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20skiers%20have%20faced%20the%20wrath%20of%20deadly%20avalanches%20in