0here%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fintroducing-india-black-boxed%5C%22%3EIntroduction%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fwhat-do-we-really-know-about-indias-gdp%5C%22%3EPart%20I%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fwhat-we-know-about-indias-post-covid-economy-recovery-and-rising-inequality%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20II%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcomptroller-auditor-general-review-2014-2023-india-black-boxed%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20III%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-union-govt-is-slowly-but-surely-blurring-indias-federal-structure%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20IV%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-sabka-saath-sabka-vikas-hoax%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20V%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-election-commissions-faqs-on-evm-vvpats-dont-clear-cloud-of-suspicion-over-electoral-process%5C%22%3Efirst%20part%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20aimed%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20certain%20responses%20provided%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20in%20its%20revised%20set%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fevm-faq-new%5C%22%3E100%20FAQs%3C%2Fa%3E%20(frequently%20asked%20questions)%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20unsatisfactory%20they%20are.%20The%20ECI%20released%20these%20updated%20FAQs%20on%20its%20website%20in%20January%20of%20this%20year%2C%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20addressing%20all%20doubts%20regarding%20these%20electoral%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20compared%20with%20the%20information%20contained%20in%20publicly%20available%20official%20documents%2C%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20claims%20about%20the%20design%2C%20and%20functioning%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20and%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20units%2C%20raise%20more%20suspicion%20instead%20of%20resolving%20persistent%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20sequel%2C%20I%20address%20additional%20claims%20by%20ECI%2C%20considering%20the%20VVPAT%20patent-related%20documents%20and%20information%20revealed%20in%20response%20to%20formal%20requests%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%202005%20(RTI%20Act).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20piece%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20examined%20the%20following%20grey%20areas%20in%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20FAQs%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20is%20the%20correct%20expanded%20form%20of%20VVPAT%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDo%20we%20know%20enough%20about%20the%20microcontrollers%20used%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20correct%20expanded%20form%20of%20VVPAT%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20FAQ%20%231%2C%20the%20ECI%20addresses%20the%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20an%20EVM%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEVM%20stands%20for%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine.%20It%20is%20a%20device%20used%20to%20electronically%20record%20and%20count%20votes%20cast%20in%20elections.%20The%20Indian%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%20(EVM)%20system%20is%20also%20termed%20as%20ECI-EVM%2C%20meaning%20an%20EVM%20specifically%20designed%2C%20manufactured%20and%20used%20for%20Elections%20as%20per%20election%20procedure%20and%20rules%20framed%20by%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20and%20documented%20in%20manual%20on%20EVM%2C%20so%20as%20to%20differentiate%20it%20from%20EVMs%20used%20in%20other%20countries.%20ECI%20%E2%80%93%20EVM%20consists%20of%20Ballot%20Unit%20(BU)%2C%20Control%20Unit%20(CU)%20and%20the%20later%20added%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ECI%2C%20VVPAT%20stands%20for%20%E2%80%9CVoter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%E2%80%9D.%20The%20reader%20is%20expected%20to%20believe%20that%20this%20is%20the%20correct%20expansion%20of%20that%20abbreviation.%20However%20other%20official%20documents%20tell%20a%20different%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20specific%20mention%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98VVPAT%E2%80%99%20or%20its%20expansion%20in%20the%20primary%20election%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20law%20which%20governs%20the%20conduct%20of%20elections%20and%20voting%20in%20India%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flddashboard.legislative.gov.in%2Felectionlawsrelated%2Frepresentation-people-act-1951-act-no-43-1951%5C%22%3Ethe%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951%3C%2Fa%3E%20(RPA).%20The%20lone%20provision%20which%20enables%20the%20use%20of%20electronic%20voting%20in%20elections%20to%20parliament%20and%20the%20State%20Legislatures%20is%20Section%2061A%20is%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C61A%20%E2%80%93%20voting%20machines%20at%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20Notwithstanding%20anything%20contained%20in%20this%20Act%20or%20the%20rules%20made%20thereunder%2C%20the%20giving%20and%20recording%20of%20votes%20by%20voting%20machines%20in%20such%20manner%20as%20may%20be%20prescribed%2C%20may%20be%20adopted%20in%20such%20constituency%20or%20constituencies%20as%20the%20Election%20Commission%20may%2C%20having%20regard%20to%20the%20circumstances%20of%20each%20case%2C%20specify.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98voting%20machine%E2%80%99%20means%20any%20machine%20or%20apparatus%20whether%20operated%20electronically%20or%20otherwise%20used%20for%20giving%20or%20recording%20of%20votes%20and%20any%20reference%20to%20a%20ballot%20box%20or%20ballot%20paper%20in%20this%20Act%20or%20the%20rules%20made%20thereunder%20shall%2C%20save%20as%20otherwise%20provided%2C%20be%20construed%20as%20including%20a%20reference%20to%20such%20voting%20machine%20wherever%20such%20voting%20machine%20is%20used%20at%20any%20election.%E2%80%9D%20(This%20provision%20was%20inserted%20through%20an%20amendment%20in%201989.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20reference%20to%20VVPATs%20in%20the%20above%20provision%2C%20nor%20can%20it%20be%20found%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flegislative.gov.in%2Fmanual-of-election-law-volume-ii%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20Rules%2C%201961%3C%2Fa%3E%20(CoER)%2C%20which%20contains%20the%20details%20of%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20RPA%20will%20be%20implemented.%20In%202013%2C%20a%20proviso%20each%20to%20Rule%2049A%20and%2049M%20and%20two%20new%20rules%20%E2%80%93%2049MA%20and%2056D%20%E2%80%93%20were%20introduced%20through%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20CoER%2C%20to%20facilitate%20the%20use%20of%20VVPATs%20in%20conjunction%20with%20EVMs.%20(Other%20relevant%20rules%20were%20also%20tweaked%20to%20incorporate%20reference%20to%20this%20change%20in%20the%20electronic%20voting%20and%20counting%20system).%20The%20contents%20of%20these%20statutory%20insertions%20are%20also%20hyperlinked%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20FAQs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20is%20noteworthy%20in%20these%20amendments%20is%20the%20complete%20absence%20of%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9CVVPAT%E2%80%9D%20or%20an%20expansion%20of%20this%20abbreviation.%20Instead%2C%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Cprinter%20for%20paper%20trail%E2%80%9D%20or%20its%20derivations%20are%20used%20in%20the%20amendments.%20So%2C%20to%20the%20best%20of%20our%20knowledge%2C%20the%20nomenclature%20%E2%80%9CVoter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%E2%80%9D%20has%20no%20statutory%20mention%2C%20either%20in%20the%201989%20amendment%20to%20the%20RPA%20or%20in%20the%202013%20amendments%20to%20the%20CoER.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20the%20ECI%20coin%20this%20phrase%20and%20the%20related%20abbreviation%20is%20a%20question%20which%20is%20not%20explained%20in%20its%20FAQs%20or%20the%20related%20Annexures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-anatomy-of-an-electronic-voting-machine-what-we-know-and-what-we-dont%5C%22%3E%20The%20Anatomy%20of%20an%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%3A%20What%20We%20Know%20and%20What%20We%20Don%E2%80%99t%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVVPAT%20is%20expanded%20differently%20in%20the%20patent-related%20records%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20answer%20to%20FAQ%20%237%2C%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Limited%20(BEL)%2C%20which%20comes%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20and%20Electronics%20Corporation%20of%20India%20Limited%20(ECIL)%2C%20which%20comes%20under%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%2C%20have%20a%20duopoly%20on%20the%20supply%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20for%20parliamentary%20and%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20discussed%20in%20the%20first%20part%2C%20only%20BEL%20has%20been%20officially%20granted%20a%20patent%20for%20the%20production%20of%20VVPATs%20in%20May%202022.%20(This%20was%20done%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EECIL%E2%80%99s%20patent%20application%20for%20a%20VVPAT%20machine%20is%20not%20available%20on%20this%20database%2C%20so%20it%20may%20be%20presumed%20that%20there%20is%20some%20working%20arrangement%20between%20the%20two%20CPSUs%20for%20manufacturing%20the%20VVPAT%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20copy%20of%20the%20order%20granting%20the%20patent%20to%20BEL%20by%20the%20Controller%20General%20of%20Patents%2C%20Designs%2C%20Trademarks%2C%20and%20Geographical%20Indications%20mentions%20the%20expansion%20of%20VVPAT%20as%20%E2%80%9CVoter%20%3Cem%3EVerified%3C%2Fem%3E%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%E2%80%9D%20and%20not%20%E2%80%9CVoter%20%3Cem%3EVerifiable%3C%2Fem%3E%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImages%20of%20the%20patent%20order%20and%20its%20communication%20to%20BEL%20by%20the%20Chennai%20Patents%20Office%20testify%20to%20this%20fact%20%3Cem%3E(see%20images%201%20and%202%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131632%2FImage-1-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131632%2FImage-1-1.jpg%20849w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131632%2FImage-1-1-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131632%2FImage-1-1-724x1024.jpg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698148%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%201.%20A%20copy%20of%20the%20government%20order%20granting%20the%20VVPAT%20patent%20and%20its%20communication%20to%20BEL%20through%20their%20Patent%20Agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131747%2FImage-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22835%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131747%2FImage-2.jpg%20835w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131747%2FImage-2-228x300.jpg%20228w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131747%2FImage-2-777x1024.jpg%20777w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698150%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221100%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%202.%20A%20copy%20of%20the%20government%20order%20granting%20the%20VVPAT%20patent%20and%20its%20communication%20to%20BEL%20through%20their%20Patent%20Agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20phrase%20%E2%80%9CVoter%20%3Cem%3EVerified%3C%2Fem%3E%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%E2%80%9D%20is%20also%20recorded%20on%20the%20patent%20certificate%20granted%20to%20BEL%20as%20part%20of%20the%20decision-making%20procedure%20%3Cem%3E(see%20image%203%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20case%20readers%20begin%20to%20speculate%2C%20the%20Patents%20Office%20may%20have%20made%20an%20error%20in%20the%20name%20due%20to%20bureaucratic%20procedures%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20worth%20noting%20that%20this%20is%20precisely%20how%20BEL%20named%20the%20VVPAT%20in%20the%20complete%20specifications%20submitted%20along%20with%20the%20patent%20application%20%3Cem%3E(see%20image%204%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21133241%2Fimage-1850.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21133241%2Fimage-1850.png%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21133241%2Fimage-1850-300x210.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698159%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22448%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%203%20and%204%3A%20A%20copy%20of%20the%20patent%20certificate%20issued%20and%20the%20front%20page%20of%20the%20VVPAT%E2%80%99s%3Cbr%3Ecomplete%20specifications%20submitted%20by%20BEL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20this%20significant%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReaders%20might%20call%20this%20nitpicking.%20%E2%80%9CVerifiable%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cverified%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20what%20difference%20does%20it%20make%20as%20long%20as%20the%20VVPAT%20machine%20does%20what%20it%20is%20required%20to%20do%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20question%20I%20raised%20before%20the%20concluding%20segment%20of%20the%20first%20part%2C%20which%20concerned%20the%20vote%20that%20must%20be%20counted%2C%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20semantic%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20%E2%80%9Cverifiable%E2%80%9D%20only%20refers%20to%20the%20potential%20of%20the%20machine%20%E2%80%93%20to%20show%20a%20slip%20recording%20the%20name%2C%20symbol%2C%20and%20serial%20number%20in%20whose%20favour%20the%20voter%20clicked%20on%20the%20Ballot%20Unit%20(BU)%20so%20that%20he%20or%20she%20may%20be%20satisfied%20with%20it%20and%20nothing%20more.%20The%20term%20%E2%80%9Cverified%E2%80%9D%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20indicates%20a%20certainty%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20slip%20has%20been%20verified%20by%20the%20voter%20before%20it%20cuts%20and%20falls%20down%20into%20the%20Drop%20Box%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20it%20not%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20that%20must%20be%20counted%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvote%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20the%20voter%20verifies%20as%20a%20correct%20record%20of%20his%20or%20her%20choice%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20electronic%20tally%20recorded%20in%20the%20control%20unit%20(CU)%3F%20This%20is%20why%20use%20of%20the%20correct%20nomenclature%20becomes%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EECI%E2%80%99s%20longwinded%20answers%20to%20FAQs%20%2362%20and%2063%20based%20on%20its%20defensive%20claims%20of%20scientific%20sampling%20of%20five%20VVPAT%20Units%2C%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20tallying%20those%20slips%20with%20the%20candidate%20totals%20from%20the%20CU%2C%20are%20simply%20unconvincing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20we%20know%20enough%20about%20the%20microcontrollers%20used%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrocontrollers%20form%20the%20nerve%20centre%20of%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo.%20Extracts%20from%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20FAQs%2C%20which%20explain%20what%20the%20microcontrollers%20do%2C%20are%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFAQ%20%2342%20%3C%2Fem%3Esays%2C%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20ECI%20says%20an%20EVM%20can%20be%20programmed%20only%20once%2C%20making%20hacking%20unlikely.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20reports%20that%20it%20can%20be%20programmed%20several%20times.%20There%20are%20other%20reports%20saying%20that%20EVM%20machines%20can%20be%20manipulated%20by%20connecting%20it%20to%20cell%20phones%2C%20Bluetooth%20devices%2C%20replacing%20parts%20of%20it%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20manipulation%2C%20apart%20from%20physical%20replacement%20of%20it%20by%20other%20EVMs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20query%20is%20explained%20as%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ECI-EVM%20use%20secure%20controllers%20which%20can%20disable%20further%20programming%20after%20a%20step%20known%20as%20one-time-programming%20(OTP).%20%3Cem%3EThe%20technical%20information%20about%20the%20micro%20controllers%20is%20available%20in%20public%20domain%20and%20can%20be%20accessed%20on%20the%20website%20of%20micro%20controller%20manufacturers%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFAQ%20%2346%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20claimed%20that%20EVM%20machines%20can%20be%20manipulated%20by%20connecting%20it%20to%20cell%20phones%2C%20Bluetooth%20devices%2C%20replacing%20parts%20of%20it%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20manipulation%2C%20apart%20from%20physical%20replacement%20of%20it%20by%20other%20EVMs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20query%20is%20explained%20as%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20claim%20is%20baseless%20and%20unscientific%20claim.%20The%20technical%20information%20about%20the%20microcontrollers%20is%20available%20in%20public%20domain%20and%20can%20be%20accessed%20on%20the%20website%20of%20microcontroller%20manufacturers.%20The%20EVMs%20%2F%20VVPATs%20use%20controllers%20which%20are%20One%20Time%20Programmable%20(OTP).%20This%20feature%20is%20activated%20by%20a%20code%20%2Fcommand%2C%20fed%20via%20a%20software%20program%2C%20and%20in%20the%20first%20time%20run%20at%20power%20%E2%80%98on%E2%80%99%20sets%20an%20internal%20register%20to%20shut%20off%20any%20re-programmability%20capability.%20%3Cu%3EThe%20code%20%2F%20command%20and%20procedure%20are%20also%20available%20in%20public%20domain%20in%20the%20datasheets%2F%20application%20notes%20on%20use%20of%20these%20microcontrollers%3C%2Fu%3E%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFAQ%20%2348%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CCan%20the%20details%20of%20the%20EVM%20microcontrollers%20be%20explained%20along%20with%20the%20OTP%20features%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20explained%20as%2C%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20use%20standard%20microcontrollers%20available%20off%20the%20shelf%20and%20hence%20all%20information%20on%20the%20microcontrollers%20is%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20via%20manufacturers%E2%80%99%20data%20sheets%2F%20application%20notes%20and%20user%20manuals.%20The%20One%20Time%20Programmable%20(OTP)%20feature%20is%20not%20activated%20by%20any%20hardware%20or%20pin-based%20signal%2Fcommand%20at%20external%20pins%20of%20the%20microcontrollers%2C%20rather%20this%20code%2F%20command%20is%20fed%20via%20a%20software%20programme%20and%20in%20the%20first%20time%20%E2%80%9Crun%E2%80%9D%20at%20power%20on%20sets%20an%20internal%20register%20to%20shut%20off%20any%20re-programmability.%20Once%20this%20is%20done%20the%20programme%20cannot%20be%20changed.%20%3Cu%3EThe%20procedure%20is%20available%20in%20public%20domain%20in%20the%20datasheets%20%2F%20user%20manuals%20on%20use%20of%20the%20microcontrollers%3C%2Fu%3E.%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20asserts%2C%20not%20once%20but%20thrice%2C%20that%20information%20about%20microcontrollers%20used%20in%20the%20EVM%20is%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20It%20also%20says%20that%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20purchase%20them%20off%20the%20shelf.%20That%20may%20be%20so%20and%20I%20do%20not%20have%20any%20reason%20to%20dispute%20that%20claim.%20But%20do%20we%20know%20from%20which%20manufacturer%E2%80%99s%20shelf%20these%20companies%20buy%20the%20microcontrollers%3F%20Neither%20the%20ECI%20nor%20the%20two%20companies%20have%20publicly%20disclosed%20the%20names%20of%20the%20microcontroller%20manufacturers%2Fsuppliers%20on%20their%20own.%20The%20only%20time%20we%20officially%20got%20to%20know%20of%20the%20identity%20of%20one%20such%20manufacturer%2Fsupplier%20was%20from%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20one%20of%20my%20RTI%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbel-refuses-to-disclose-evm-vvpat-data-even-after-demanding-fees-what-does-it-mean%5C%22%3EBEL%20Refuses%20to%20Disclose%20EVM%2C%20VVPAT%20Data%20Even%20After%20Demanding%20Fees.%20What%20Does%20It%20Mean%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202019%2C%20identical%20RTI%20applications%20were%20filed%20with%20BEL%2C%20seeking%20the%20complete%20list%20of%20manufacturers%20of%20microcontrollers%20used%20in%20the%20latest%20generation%20(M3)%20EVMs%2C%20along%20with%20their%20postal%20addresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Public%20Information%20Officer%20(CPIO)%20replied%20with%20the%20model%20number%20of%20the%20microcontroller%20used%20in%20the%20EVMs%20%3Cem%3E(see%20image%205%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20ECIL%E2%80%99s%20CPIO%20denied%20access%20to%20the%20same%20information%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20%E2%80%98classified%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20invoked%20the%20national%20security%20exemption%20under%20Section%208(1)(a)%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act.%20%3Cem%3E(See%20image%206%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5