061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21144506%2Fimage-1853.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22616%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21144506%2Fimage-1853.png%20616w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21144506%2Fimage-1853-300x209.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698179%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22430%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%207%20%26amp%3B%208%3A%20ECIL%20FAA%E2%80%99s%20order%20post%20CIC%20decision%20and%20CPIO%E2%80%99s%20subsequent%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20prolonged%20RTI%20interventions%2C%20the%20ECI%20cannot%20claim%20with%20a%20straight%20face%20that%20information%20about%20the%20microcontrollers%20is%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Even%20if%20it%20were%2C%20voters%20can%20only%20access%20it%20if%20the%20names%20of%20the%20manufacturers%2Fsuppliers%20are%20made%20public.%20Otherwise%2C%20this%20information%20remains%20trapped%20in%20a%20black%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-commissions-faqs-on-evms-dont-really-address-major-design-deficiencies%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20FAQs%20on%20EVMs%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Really%20Address%20Major%20Design%20Deficiencies%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20microcontrollers%2C%20used%20by%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%2C%20only%20one-time-programmable%20(OTP)%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20was%20my%20initial%20foray%20into%20the%20world%20of%20EVMs%2C%20the%20query%20was%20negligently%20drafted%2C%20leaving%20out%20a%20reference%20to%20VVPAT%20in%20the%20RTI%20query%20relating%20to%20microcontrollers.%20I%20ended%20up%20asking%20only%20about%20EVM%20microcontrollers%2C%20as%20I%20had%20not%20read%20the%20relevant%20patent%20documents%20about%20VVPATs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20discussed%20in%20the%20first%20part%2C%20we%20know%20for%20a%20fact%20that%20both%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20were%20granted%20patents%20for%20the%20EVMs%20in%202006.%20Both%20companies%20disclosed%20the%20presence%20of%20microcontrollers%20in%20the%20CUs%20of%20their%20EVMs%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20need%20under%20the%20patents%20law%20to%20mention%20the%20names%20of%20manufacturers%20of%20any%20component%20of%20the%20machine%20sought%20to%20be%20patented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20while%20BEL%20claimed%20that%20the%20microcontroller%20it%20was%20using%20was%20one-time-programmable%20(OTP)%2C%20ECIL%20staked%20no%20such%20claim%20%3Cem%3E(see%20images%209%20and%2010%20below).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22153702%2Fimage-1854.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22623%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22153702%2Fimage-1854.png%20623w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22153702%2Fimage-1854-300x215.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698357%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22447%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EExtract%20from%20the%20complete%20specifications%20about%20EVMs%20submitted%20by%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20respectively%2C%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20complete%20believer%20in%20their%20infallibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImage%209%20is%20an%20extract%20from%20the%20complete%20specifications%20of%20the%20EVM%2C%20which%20BEL%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller%2C%20where%20the%20microcontroller%20is%20described%20as%20OTP%20type.%20Image%2010%20is%20an%20extract%20from%20the%20complete%20specifications%20of%20the%20EVM%2C%20which%20ECIL%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller%2C%20where%20the%20microcontroller%20is%20not%20described%20as%20OTP%20type.%20Further%2C%20ECIL%E2%80%99s%20description%20of%20what%20the%20CU%20can%20do%20with%20its%20microcontroller%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Ccollect%2C%20record%2C%20store%2C%20count%20and%20display%20the%20votes%20when%20called%20for%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20completely%20obviates%20any%20possibility%20that%20it%20is%20one-time-programmable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20EVM%20machines%20are%20intended%20for%20repeated%20use%20across%20multiple%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20logical%20to%20assume%20that%20the%20microcontroller%20utilised%20by%20ECIL%20must%20be%20rewriteable.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20that%20the%20microcontrollers%20employed%20by%20both%20companies%20are%20of%20the%20OTP%20type%20does%20not%20appear%20very%20convincing.%20Unless%20ECIL%20has%20since%20altered%20the%20design%20of%20its%20CU%20to%20mirror%20the%20OTP-type%20microcontroller%20used%20by%20BEL%2C%20there%20is%20hardly%20any%20information%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20regarding%20such%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20many%20microcontrollers%20are%20used%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20confirmed%20from%20the%20patent-related%20documents%20discussed%20above%20that%20there%20is%20indeed%20a%20microcontroller%20within%20the%20CU%20of%20the%20EVMs%20manufactured%20by%20both%20companies.%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20patent%20application%20documents%20further%20disclose%20that%20its%20VVPAT%20machine%20also%20contains%20at%20least%20one%20microcontroller%20and%20suggest%20the%20potential%20existence%20of%20multiple%20such%20microcontrollers%20%3Cem%3E(see%20images%2011%20and%2012%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22154919%2Fimage-1855.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22631%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22154919%2Fimage-1855.png%20631w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22154919%2Fimage-1855-300x200.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698358%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22420%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%2011%20and%2012%3A%20Extracts%20from%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20complete%20specifications%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20machine%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20paragraph%20no.%200053%20of%20the%20complete%20specifications%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller%20while%20applying%20for%20a%20patent%2C%20BEL%20states%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5B0053%5D%20In%20an%20aspect%2C%20the%20sensitive%20hardware%20may%20be%20one%20or%20more%20artefacts%20such%20as%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20%3Cem%3Eone-time%20programmable%20microcontroller%2C%20associated%20storage%20comprising%20of%20computational%20program%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20sensitive%20data%20and%20configuration%20information%20among%20other%20things.%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20at%20paragraph%20no.%2000136%20of%20the%20same%20document%2C%20BEL%20states%20as%20follows%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20detailed%20description%20of%20the%20drawings%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20machine%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5B00136%5D%20In%20another%20aspect%2C%20%3Cem%3Evarious%20software%20for%20control%20and%20operation%20of%20the%20proposed%20system%20can%20be%20held%20in%20appropriately%20configured%20one%20or%20more%20controllers%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20absolutely%20secure%20formats%20so%20that%20such%20software%20may%20not%20be%20tampered%20with%2C%20without%20errors%20being%20triggered.%20%3Cu%3EMicrocontrollers%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3Cem%3Eused%20in%20the%20proposed%20system%20can%20be%20of%20one%20time%20programmable%20type%20and%20used%20to%20store%20firmware%20that%20cannot%20be%20changed%20or%20modified%20once%20fused.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20combined%20reading%20of%20the%20two%20claims%20made%20by%20BEL%20indicates%20the%20use%20of%20at%20least%20one%20more%20OTP-type%20microcontroller%20in%20its%20VVPAT%20machine%2C%20which%20is%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20microcontroller%20used%20in%20the%20CU%20of%20the%20EVM.%20That%20is%20not%20all%2C%20in%20the%20same%20document%2C%20BEL%20claims%20that%20there%20is%20another%20associated%20storage%20component%20which%20will%20contain%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccomputational%20program%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20this%20will%20be%20the%20%E2%80%98artefact%20into%20which%20the%20candidate%20names%2C%20symbols%20and%20serial%20numbers%20are%20loaded%20during%20every%20election.%20So%2C%20this%20artefact%20(not%20being%20a%20hardware%20or%20software%20engineer%2C%20I%20hesitate%20to%20call%20them%20a%20%E2%80%98microcontroller%E2%80%99)%20cannot%20possibly%20be%20OTP-type.%20Who%20is%20supplying%20this%20artefact%2Fdevice%20is%20a%20mystery%20hidden%20inside%20a%20black%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevm-voting-machine-election-polls%5C%22%3EThe%20Term%20%E2%80%98EVM%E2%80%99%20No%20Longer%20Serves%20Us.%20We%20Need%20to%20Understand%20%E2%80%98Electronic%20Voting%20Systems%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20memory%20does%20NXP%20microcontroller%20have%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20CPIO%20wittingly%20or%20unwittingly%20disclosed%20the%20model%20number%20of%20the%20microcontroller%20in%20response%20to%20the%202019%20RTI%20application.%20The%20webpage%20of%20the%20company%20NXP%2C%20from%20which%20BEL%20purchased%20the%20microcontroller%2C%20explains%20that%20the%20model%20type%2C%20NXP-MK61FX512VMD12%2C%20features%20not%20just%20one%2C%20but%20three%20types%20of%20memory.%20Among%20these%2C%20one%20is%20OTP%20type%2C%20and%20another%20is%20rewriteable%2C%20akin%20to%20the%20memory%20found%20in%20commonly%20used%20pen%2Fflash%20drives%20%3Cem%3E(see%20images%2013%20and%2014%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22160027%2Fimage-1856.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22836%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22160027%2Fimage-1856.png%20675w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22160027%2Fimage-1856-300x204.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698361%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22567%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%2013%20and%2014%3A%20Product%20description%20of%20the%20NXP-MK61FX512VMD12%20microcontroller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-anatomy-of-an-electronic-voting-machine-what-we-know-and-what-we-dont%5C%22%3Emade%20this%20information%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20media%20covered%20it%20widely%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20always%20labelled%20the%20microcontroller%20as%20an%20OTP-type.%20It%20is%20quite%20a%20relief%20to%20see%20the%20Commission%20acknowledging%20this%20fact%20in%20its%20FAQ%20%2353%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cstrong%3EFAQ53.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20the%20VVPAT%20have%20a%20programmable%20memory%3F%20If%20yes%2C%20then%20at%20what%20stages%20in%20the%20election%20process%20is%20it%20accessed%20by%20an%20external%20device%3F%20If%20no%2C%20then%20where%20are%20the%20names%20and%20symbols%20of%20the%20candidates%20stored%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20for%20it%20to%20print%20the%20same%20in%20theVVPAT%20slip%20later%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswer%3A%20%3Cem%3EA%20VVPAT%20has%20two%20different%20memories.%20One%2C%20where%20the%20program%20instructions%20are%20kept%20for%20the%20microcontrollers%2C%20is%20One%20Time%20Programmed%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E(OTP).%20The%20VVPAT%20firmware%20is%20stored%20in%20the%20One%20Time%20Programmed%20memory%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EAfter%20the%20firmware%20is%20ported%20in%20the%20microcontroller%20at%20the%20manufacturers%E2%80%99%20site%2C%20no%20changes%20in%20the%20program%20are%20possible%20subsequently.%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20other%20memory%20is%20for%20storing%20graphical%20images%20containing%20serial%20number%2C%20name%2C%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidates%20as%20data%3C%2Fu%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThis%20is%20done%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20symbol%20loading%20unit%2C%20during%20the%20commissioning%20of%20VVPATs%20before%20each%20election.%20Live%20display%20of%20the%20symbols%20being%20loaded%20into%20the%20VVPAT%20is%20done%20during%20the%20Commissioning%20process%20in%20presence%20of%20candidates%2Ftheir%20representatives%20to%20make%20the%20process%20more%20transparent.%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20the%20ECI%20does%20not%20tell%20us%20is%20whether%20the%20same%20NXP-manufactured%20microcontroller%20is%20used%20in%20the%20CU%20of%20the%20EVM%20and%20also%20the%20VVPAT%20(for%20two%20types%20of%20uses%20%E2%80%93%20one%20for%20programme%20instructions%20and%20another%20for%20storing%20the%20candidate-related%20information%20and%20images%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20only%20one%20of%20the%20NXP%20chips%20one-time%20programmed%20while%20the%20others%20are%20rewriteable%3F%20Or%20do%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20use%20other%20brands%20of%20rewriteable%20microcontrollers%3F%20Is%20the%20pattern%20of%20microcontroller%20usage%20similar%20in%20both%20BEL-%20and%20ECIL-manufactured%20machines%3F%20ECIL%20did%20not%20claim%20in%20its%20EVM%20patent%20documents%20that%20the%20microcontroller%20it%20uses%20are%20OTP%20type.%20Has%20that%20changed%20now%3F%20The%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20FAQs%20are%20silent%20about%20these%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern%20is%20the%20November%202023%20media%20revelation%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farstechnica.com%2Fsecurity%2F2023%2F11%2Fhackers-spent-2-years-looting-secrets-of-chipmaker-nxp-before-being-detected%2F%5C%22%3ENXP%20was%20the%20victim%20of%20an%20espionage%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%202017%20and%202020.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20company%20reportedly%20neglected%20to%20inform%20its%20customers%20individually%20about%20these%20developments.%20It%20is%20confirmed%20that%20at%20least%20BEL%2C%20if%20not%20ECIL%2C%20procured%20microcontrollers%20from%20NXP%20during%20this%20period.%20The%20extent%20to%20which%20this%20may%20have%20affected%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20units%20produced%20by%20BEL%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20supplier%20year%20after%20year%2C%20remains%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20poses%20a%20significant%20national%20security%20concern%20that%20both%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20the%20companies%20utilising%20NXP%20microcontrollers%20must%20address%20to%20all%20voters%20before%20the%20next%20round%20of%20elections.%20When%20crucial%20information%20is%20withheld%20within%20a%20black%20box%2C%20suspicions%20will%20only%20continue%20to%20linger.%20These%20elections%20belong%20to%20us%2C%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20units%20are%20machines%20funded%20and%20utilized%20by%20us%2C%20the%20people.%20Hence%2C%20WE%20THE%20PEOPLE%20have%20the%20right%20to%20demand%20more%20transparency%20than%20what%20the%20ECI%20has%20disclosed%20thus%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVenkatesh%20Nayak%20is%20director%2C%20Commonwealth%20Human%20Rights%20Initiative%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20All%20facts%20narrated%20above%20are%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Views%20expressed%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708605051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F04112925%2FVoting_machine_in_India.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fevms-and-vvpats-why-suspicions-persist-and-wont-subside-yet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20discrepancy%20in%20the%20expansion%20of%20VVPAT%2C%20recorded%20as%20%26quot%3BVoter%20Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%26quot%3B%20in%20patent-related%20records%2C%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20legitimacy%20and%20functioning%20of%20these%20voting%20systems.%20Moreover%2C%20do%20we%20know%20enough%20about%20the%20microcontrollers%20used%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fevms-and-vvpats-why-suspicions-persist-and-wont-subside-yet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%20The%20Only%20Certainty%20After%20a%20Rigged%20Election%20Is%20Chaos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22145025%2FUntitled-design-7.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20two%20weeks%20after%20one%20of%20the%20most%20tainted%20elections%20in%20the%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20checkered%20parliamentary%20history%2C%20a%20coalition%20government%20is%20in%20sight.%20But%20the%20only%20certainty%20that%20has%20emerged%20is%20instability%20and%20political%20chaos.%20And%20it%20may%20only%20get%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20aphorism%20goes%20that%20the%20Pakistan%20army%20has%20never%20won%20a%20war%20and%20never%20lost%20an%20election.%20The%20army%20might%20not%20have%20lost%20this%20one%20either%20but%20appears%20to%20have%20botched%20the%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brass%20had%20intended%20and%20plotted%20for%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan%20to%20be%20routed%20at%20the%20polls%2C%20thus%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20purging%20him%20out%20of%20the%20political%20system.%20It%20envisaged%20a%20new%20dispensation%20along%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.jang.com.pk%2Fdetail%2F624671%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fe.jang.com.pk%2Fdetail%2F624671%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1xUtPI6MJWSVCgvH5thHBE%5C%22%3Eso-called%20Bangladesh%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20diarchal%20controlled%20democracy%20in%20which%20the%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PMLN)%20alone%2C%20or%20in%20a%20coalition%20with%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20(PPP)%20and%20others%2C%20would%20form%20a%20stable%20government.%20But%20the%20election%20results%20stunned%20everyone%2C%20including%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20planners%20and%20conventional%20political%20prognosticators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependent%20candidates%20backed%20by%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%20Tehrik-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20party%2C%20swept%20the%20polls%20for%20the%20Khyber-Pakhtunkhwa%E2%80%99s%20(KP)%20provincial%20legislature%20and%20won%20a%20plurality%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20military%20establishment%20had%20thrown%20everything%20but%20the%20kitchen%20sink%20at%20its%20former%20prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%20Khan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-election-no-matter-who-wins-the-army-will-rule-the-roost%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-election-no-matter-who-wins-the-army-will-rule-the-roost%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1VwNRXajI4eXSGItW4wpDw%5C%22%3Eto%20keep%20him%20from%20returning%20to%20power%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20PTI%2C%20with%20its%20electoral%20machinery%20already%20depleted%20after%20the%20army%20induced%20defections%20and%20break-away%20factions%2C%20was%20kept%20from%20running%20as%20a%20party%20by%20denying%20it%20an%20election%20symbol.%20Khan%2C%20who%20has%20already%20been%20in%20jail%2C%20was%20slapped%20with%20egregious%20sentences%2C%20including%20a%20grotesque%20one%20for%20an%20unlawful%20marriage%20under%20Islamic%20conventions%2C%20just%20days%20before%20the%20polls.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20election%20campaign%20was%20run%20by%20its%20third%20and%20fourth-tier%20leadership%2C%20comprising%20mostly%20of%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20made%20effective%20use%20of%20the%20new%20media%20platforms%20like%20TikTok%20to%20run%20campaign%20ads%20and%20held%20virtual%20rallies%20on%20Twitter%20and%20Facebook.%20In%20a%20first%20for%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20party%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Fvideo%2F2023%2Fdec%2F18%2Fpakistans-imran-khan-uses-ai-crafted-speech-to-call-for-votes-from-prison-video%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Fvideo%2F2023%2Fdec%2F18%2Fpakistans-imran-khan-uses-ai-crafted-speech-to-call-for-votes-from-prison-video%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw22KQ88aZeQF6KJroOYYrnn%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20to%20generate%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20speeches%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20simulating%20his%20voice%20calling%20for%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20cadres%20deployed%20WhatsApp%20and%20other%20electronic%20modalities%20in%20their%20get-out-the-vote%20efforts.%20The%20exercise%20was%20largely%20dismissed%20by%20the%20pundits%20and%20political%20opponents%20as%20mere%20social%20media%20hype.%20Not%20leaving%20anything%20to%20chance%2C%20the%20caretaker%20government%20had%20shut%20the%20mobile%20phone%20system%20and%20internet%20services%20on%20the%20polling%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fwas-there-anything-truly-historic-about-pakistans-2024-elections%5C%22%3EWas%20There%20Anything%20Truly%20Historic%20About%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%202024%20Elections%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20preliminary%20results%20started%20coming%20in%2C%20the%20PTI-backed%20independents%20seemed%20unstoppable.%20While%20assorted%20television%20and%20news%20outlets%20were%20making%20projections%2C%20the%20official%20provisional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-08%2Fpakistan-poll-results-delayed-as-imran-khan-s-party-claims-win%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-08%2Fpakistan-poll-results-delayed-as-imran-khan-s-party-claims-win%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw051-FMTITb6FAJ2mWRCand%5C%22%3Eresults%20were%20nowhere%20to%20be%20found%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20old%20tactic%20of%20tinkering%20with%20the%20election%20results%20when%20it%20fails%20to%20achieve%20the%20desired%20outcome%20through%20pre-poll%20rigging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Pashtun%20and%20Baloch%20nationalist%20parties%20cried%20foul.%20They%20alleged%20gross%20discrepancies%20between%20the%20vote%20count%20submitted%20by%20the%20presiding%20officers%20at%20the%20polling%20stations%20and%20the%20consolidated%20results%20released%20by%20the%20returning%20officers%20at%20the%20constituency%20level.%20But%20it%20all%20seemed%20like%20an%20amateur%20hour%20at%20the%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20rigging%20headquarters%2C%20which%20was%20playing%20catch-up%20to%20stymie%20the%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20outright%20victory.%20Khan%2C%20however%2C%20declared%20triumph%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F02%2F11%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fimran-khan-artificial-intelligence-pakistan.html%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F02%2F11%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fimran-khan-artificial-intelligence-pakistan.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1v0-jUbI5GdHpT5QPM85GM%5C%22%3Espeech%20generated%20by%20A.I%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20visibly%20crestfallen%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20who%20was%20seeking%20a%20fourth%20stint%20as%20the%20PM%2C%20also%20a%20made%20a%20subdued%20speech%20proclaiming%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20remarkable%20bounce%20back%20was%20a%20culmination%20of%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20relentless%20assault%20on%20his%20opponents%20since%20his%20ouster%20from%20power%20in%20April%202022%20through%20a%20no-confidence%20move%2C%20which%20also%20had%20a%20nod%20from%20the%20then%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20(COAS)%20Qamar%20Javed%20Bajwa.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20dogged%20offensive%20targeted%20both%20Bajwa%20and%20his%20successor%2C%20General%20Asim%20Munir%20along%20the%20way.%20When%20the%20PTI%20chief%20was%20eventually%20arrested%2C%20his%20party%20men%20even%20rioted%20against%20military%20installations%20for%20which%20both%20the%20leader%20and%20cadres%20are%20facing%20charges.%20But%20an%20undeterred%20Khan%20didn%E2%80%99t%20back%20down%20from%20railing%20against%20General%20Munir.%20He%20also%20trained%20his%20guns%20on%20the%20Pakistan%20Democratic%20Movement%20(PDM)%20coalition%20government%20comprising%20of%20the%20PMLN%20and%20the%20PPP%20that%20had%20replaced%20him%20and%20scored%20several%20bye-election%20victories%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20is%20a%20textbook%20demagogue%20who%20thrived%20in%20turmoil%20and%20successfully%20channeled%20the%20existing%20dislike%20for%20traditional%20politics%20and%20widespread%20resentment%20against%20the%20army%2C%20to%20mobilise%20his%20cult-like%20following%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20young%20voters%20that%20make%20the%20bulk%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20electorate.%20The%20results%2C%20however%2C%20also%20suggest%20pockets%20of%20support%20for%20Khan%20in%20the%20state%20machinery%2C%20including%20the%20army%2C%20which%20might%20have%20been%20a%20hurdle%20in%20the%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20completely%20steamroll%20the%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20election%20that%20was%20essentially%20fought%20along%20the%20pro%20and%20anti-Imran%20Khan%20line%2C%20the%20traditional%20political%20forces%20largely%20played%20catch%20up%20with%20him.%20The%20PMLN%2C%20despite%20securing%20a%20majority%20in%20its%20traditional%20bastion%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20provincial%20legislature%2C%20performed%20dismally%20at%20the%20national%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENawaz%20Sharif%2C%20who%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67167601%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67167601%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw04dgkXPYTFmj_uk-CNOOMo%5C%22%3Ereturned%20from%20a%20self-exile%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20London%20last%20October%2C%20to%20lead%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%2C%20could%20not%20lift%20its%20sagging%20fortunes.%20He%20had%20tried%20to%20put%20himself%20between%20the%20electorate%20and%20the%20Shehbaz%20Sharif-led%20PDM%20government%E2%80%99s%20abysmal%20performance%2C%20during%20which%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FEconomy%2FInflation%2FPakistan-inflation-hits-record-35-as-IMF-talks-drag-on%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FEconomy%2FInflation%2FPakistan-inflation-hits-record-35-as-IMF-talks-drag-on%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw35FrdaZb8TbKboGIr-5syj%5C%22%3Einflation%20had%20risen%20to%2035%25%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20Pakistan%20narrowly%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-07-12%2Fpakistan-secures-final-imf-approval-for-3-billion-bailout%23xj4y7vzkg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-07-12%2Fpakistan-secures-final-imf-approval-for-3-billion-bailout%2523xj4y7vzkg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1oHyItTNYX449cJg-5gpTQ%5C%22%3Edodged%20the%20economic%20default%20bullet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20Sharif%2C%20ostensibly%20under%20pressure%20from%20his%20own%20brother%20and%20other%20partymen%2C%20opted%20to%20shelve%20his%20previous%20anti-establishment%20plank%20and%20avoided%20questioning%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20meddling%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20combined%20weight%20of%20PDM%2FPMLN%E2%80%99s%2016-month%20incumbency%2C%20reliance%20on%201990s-style%20patronage%20politics%2C%20and%20abandoning%20a%20principled%20position%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20army%2C%20was%20too%20much%20even%20for%20Sharif%20to%20pull.%20Pashtun%20and%20Baloch%20nationalist%20forces%2C%20which%20had%20entered%20the%20field%20divided%20into%20several%20parties%20and%20groups%2C%20also%20faced%20the%20brunt%20of%20rigging%2C%20especially%20in%20Balochistan%20and%20the%20former%20tribal%20districts%20of%20KP%2C%20where%20assorted%20pro-army%20candidates%20got%20the%20results%20fixed%20in%20their%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muttahida%20Qaumi%20Movement%20(MQM)%2C%20which%20claims%20to%20represent%20the%20Urdu-speaking%20population%20of%20urban%20Sindh%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20benefitted%20from%20the%20establishment%20trying%20to%20offset%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20lead%20in%20Punjab%20and%20KP%2C%20and%20got%20awarded%20a%20handful%20of%20seats.%20The%20only%20traditional%20party%20that%20escaped%20rather%20unscathed%20was%20the%20former%20president%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20and%20his%20son%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%E2%80%99s%20PPP.%20The%20PPP%20has%20perfected%20the%20art%20of%20positioning%20itself%20as%20a%20Sindhi%20nationalist%20party%20in%20its%20home%20province%20while%20posturing%20as%20the%20great%20federalist%20force%20at%20the%20center.%20It%20was%20able%20to%20retain%20a%20not%20only%20a%20comfortable%20majority%20in%20Sindh%20province%2C%20but%20also%20made%20inroads%20in%20Balochistan%20by%20enlisting%20several%20army-allied%20tribal%20politicians.%20The%20PPP%20was%20perhaps%20the%20only%20party%20that%20actually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPPP_Org%2Fstatus%2F1759292948393402840%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPPP_Org%2Fstatus%2F1759292948393402840%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1OQa4ehQ9iSYaZ8Bnpe6LA%5C%22%3Ecelebrated%20Yaum-e-Tashakkur%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0or%20a%20thanksgiving%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20said%20and%20done%2C%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20the%20PTI%20won%2093%20seats%2C%20the%20PML-N%2075%2C%20the%20PPP%2054%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20MQM%20at%2017%20seats.%20Several%20ethno-nationalist%20and%20religious%20parties%20are%20in%20single%20digits.%20It%20is%20effectively%20a%20hung%20parliament%20with%20no%20party%20in%20a%20position%20to%20form%20the%20government%20on%20its%20own%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20PTI%20with%20Khan%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20negotiate%20with%20the%20others.%20The%20PTI-backed%20independent%20candidates%20are%20further%20hamstrung%20by%20the%20stipulation%20that%20unless%20they%20join%20a%20formal%20party%20that%20has%20presence%20in%20the%20national%20assembly%2C%20they%20would%20be%20deprived%20of%20the%20seats%20reserved%20for%20the%20women%20and%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PMLN%20and%20the%20PPP%20played%20hot%20potato%20with%20the%20government%20formation%2C%20knowing%20full%20well%20that%20this%20dispensation%20won%E2%80%99t%20exactly%20be%20a%20bed%20of%20roses.%20Unwilling%20to%20sit%20atop%20a%20shaky%20government%20at%20the%20twilight%20of%20his%20political%20career%2C%20Sharif%20had%20pulled%20himself%20out%20of%20the%20race%20for%20the%20high%20office.%20He%20nominated%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%2C%20a%20known%20toady%20of%20the%20army%2C%20for%20the%20slot.%20The%20PPP%2C%20in%20a%20better%20position%20than%20ever%20to%20exact%20its%20pound%20of%20flesh%2C%20played%20hard%20to%20catch%20for%20a%20bit.%20But%20finally%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenews.com.pk%2Flatest%2F1159717-bilawal-addresses-presser-after-days-long-ppp-pml-n-govt-formation-meeting%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenews.com.pk%2Flatest%2F1159717-bilawal-addresses-presser-after-days-long-ppp-pml-n-govt-formation-meeting%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1so3Msxdl4AWRNaAydi-Jp%5C%22%3Ecoalition%20government%20was%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20as%20the%20PM%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20Asif%20Zardari%20becoming%20the%20president%20and%20assorted%20elected%20and%20appointed%20offices%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Balochistan%20government%20likely%20going%20to%20the%20PPP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20setup%20is%20essentially%20the%20second%20edition%20of%20the%20PDM%20coalition%20that%20ousted%20Khan.%20The%20arrangement%20was%20inevitable.%20Neither%20the%20two%20main%20parties%20in%20the%20coalition%20nor%20the%20General%20Munir%20who%20is%20detested%20by%20Khan%20had%20any%20great%20choices.%20They%20had%20set%20out%20to%20purge%20Khan%20from%20the%20polity%20but%20ended%20up%20with%20the%20man%20bagging%20one-third%20of%20the%20seats%20in%20the%20house.%20And%20that%20along%20with%20the%20multiple%20crises%20that%20Pakistan%20is%20already%20facing%2C%20makes%20the%20things%20more%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20hotchpotch%20government%20coming%20into%20office%2C%20as%20the%20result%20of%20an%20extremely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhrcp-web.org%2Fhrcpweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F2024-A-Tainted-Election.pdf%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fhrcp-web.org%2Fhrcpweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F2024-A-Tainted-Election.pdf%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1kD4l686B6IkjQoJLWiSvM%5C%22%3Eshady%20election%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20hardly%20the%20popular%20or%20consensus%20dispensation%20needed%20to%20tackle%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fmultiple-challenges-face-winner-pakistans-upcoming-general-election-2024-02-06%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fmultiple-challenges-face-winner-pakistans-upcoming-general-election-2024-02-06%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2Go6xrSlD2tPbcnKh4c2yB%5C%22%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20myriad%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20a%20tanking%20economy%20and%20domestic%20terrorism.%20For%20his%20part%2C%20Khan%2C%20being%20the%20quintessential%20demagogue%2C%20cannot%20function%20in%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20political%20harmony%20and%20tolerance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20one%20provincial%20government%20under%20his%20belt%20and%20a%20sizeable%20presence%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly%2C%20Khan%20is%20unlikely%20to%20back%20down.%20General%20Munir%20and%20the%20PDM%202.0%20would%20hold%20each%20other%20in%20an%20ever-tighter%20embrace%2C%20so%20long%20as%20the%20spectre%20of%20Imran%20Khan%20looms.%20The%20army%2C%20however%2C%20controls%20many%20levers%20of%20power%20and%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20legal%20travails%20are%20by%20no%20means%20over.%20How%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejunta%3C%2Fem%3E%20grapples%20with%20a%20resurgent%20Khan%20would%20be%20the%20main%20event%20and%20a%20measly%20coalition%20government%20merely%20a%20sideshow.%20Political%20chaos%20and%20uncertainty%20would%20be%20the%20name%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmohammad-taqi%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmohammad-taqi%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1ZbCnA_guSYjcQB-0rfMbU%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMohammad%20Taqi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Pakistani-American%20columnist.%20He%20tweets%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmazdaki%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmazdaki%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw02CPe39e9RAg4Jun3JXowL%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%40mazdaki%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708605035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22145025%2FUntitled-design-7.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-the-only-certainty-after-a-rigged-election-is-chaos%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20the%20public%20grapples%20with%20a%20resurgent%20Imran%20Khan%20would%20be%20the%20main%20event%20and%20a%20measly%20coalition%20government%20merely%20a%20sideshow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-the-only-certainty-after-a-rigged-election-is-chaos%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'World's%20oldest%20dog'%20stripped%20of%20Guinness%20record%20title%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708604160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F70x70%2Fskynews-bobi-leonel-costa-dog_6465236.jpg%3F20240222140242%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fguinness-world-records-oldest-dog-bobi-stripped-of-title-13078220%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bobi%2C%20who%20was%20crowned%20the%20world's%20oldest%20dog%2C%20has%20had%20his%20title%20stripped%20from%20him%20following%20controversy%20around%20his%20real%20age.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fguinness-world-records-oldest-dog-bobi-stripped-of-title-13078220%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fguinness-world-records-oldest-dog-bobi-stripped-of-title-13078220%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fguinness-world-records-oldest-dog-bobi-stripped-of-title-13078220%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAapro%20Fali%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Parsi%20Community's%20Pride%20and%20the%20Constitutional%20Authority%20With%20a%20Twinkle%20in%20His%20Eye%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21155108%2FUntitled-design-2-4.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20Parsis%20love%20to%20lay%20personal%20claim%20to%20our%20greats.%20Even%20all%20those%20with%20whom%20our%20familiarity%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20go%20beyond%20their%20public%20presence.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20%E2%80%98Apro%20George%E2%80%99%20it%20was%20a%20legit%20claim%3B%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20King%20G.%20the%20Fifth%20once%20framed%20on%20our%20drawing%20room%20wall%20along%20with%20our%20forebears%20four%20generations%20up%20the%20family%20tree%3F%20But%2C%20seriously%2C%20the%20present%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20much%20replenished%20the%20trove%20of%20the%20past%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20gaping%20hole%20grew%20wider%20with%20the%20passing%20of%20Fali%20Nariman%2C%20the%20last%20in%20that%20legion%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20legal%20greats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20one%20of%20those%20who%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20add%20his%20voice%20to%20the%20cacophony%20triggered%20by%20any%20of%20the%20many%20issues%2C%20valid%20or%20hysteria-fanned%20which%20plague%20our%20increasingly%20paranoid%20community.%20But%20when%20called%20upon%2C%20he%20gave%20unstintingly%20of%20his%20time%2C%20erudition%20%E2%80%93%20and%20reputation.%20The%20most%20recent%20was%20that%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EBombay%20Parsi%20Punchayat%20vs%20the%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20he%20steered%20an%20amicable%20solution%20to%20the%20emotionally%20sensitive%20matter%20of%20disposing%20of%20the%20corpses%20of%20Covid%20victims%3B%20the%20traditional%20manner%20was%20deemed%20violative%20of%20government%20protocols.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20deeply%20and%20as%20quietly%20he%20was%20invested%20in%20his%20own%20%E2%80%98court%E2%80%99%20was%20reflected%20in%20the%20heartfelt%20tributes%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Parsi%20Anjuman%20and%20Parzor%2C%20Shernaz%20Cama%E2%80%99s%20UNESCO-recognised%20body%20for%20the%20preservation%20of%20Parsi-Zoroastrian%20heritage%3B%20he%20was%20its%20senior%20most%20patron.%20It%20recorded%20how%20much%20%E2%80%98Fali%20Uncle%E2%80%99%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20his%20%E2%80%98sane%20advice%2C%20his%20penetrating%20questions%20and%20his%20sense%20of%20humour%E2%80%99.%20It%20thanked%20him%20for%20all%20he%20had%20done%20not%20only%20for%20Parsis%2C%20but%20the%20Delhi%20Commonwealth%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Association%2C%20and%20in%20many%20silent%20charities%20both%20for%20%E2%80%98humanity%20and%20animals%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWould%20it%20be%20too%20presumptuous%20for%20me%20to%20claim%20a%20personal%20familiarity%3F%20Yes%2C%20for%20the%20obvious%20reason%20that%20a%20mere%20hack%20must%20know%20her%20place%20vis%20a%20vis%20the%20Bhishma%20Pitamaha%20of%20jurisprudence.%20But%20then%20Fali%20himself%20kept%20his%20twinkling%20eye%20despite%20being%20the%20terror%20of%20those%20daring%20to%20take%20their%20muddying%20boots%20into%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20sanctum%20sanctorum.%20He%20who%20wrote%20those%20magisterial%20books%20and%20op-eds%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20above%20emailing%20me%20an%20appreciative%20comment%20on%20a%20particularly%20clever%20turn%20of%20phrase%20%E2%80%93%20or%2C%20on%20his%20own%20bat%2C%20sending%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20editor%20validating%20a%20piece%20of%20mine%20which%20had%20argued%20against%20the%20excesses%20of%20our%20powerful%20Parsi%20orthodoxies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20because%20of%20these%20periodic%20back-pats%20that%20I%20made%20bold%20to%20ask%20if%20I%20could%20meet%20him%20in%20Delhi%20to%20understand%20the%20legal%20nuances%20of%20the%20Nanavati%20case%20for%20my%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EIn%20Hot%20Blood%3C%2Fem%3E.%20My%20son%20was%20aghast%20at%20my%20%E2%80%98demanding%20free%20services%20of%20someone%20who%20charges%20such%20astronomical%20fees%20for%20a%20court%20appearance%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20and%20rolled%20his%20eyes%20while%20retreating%20in%20defeat%20when%20the%20great%20man%20wrote%20back%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Sure%2C%20come%20any%20time.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20I%20betook%20myself%20armed%20with%20a%20tape%20recorder%2C%20notebook%20and%20questions%20prepared%20for%20a%20lengthy%20lesson%20on%20the%20judicial%20system%20and%20even%20constitutional%20law.%20After%20all%20this%20was%20a%20surreal%20case%20which%20began%20in%20the%20illicit%20privacy%20of%20an%20extra-marital%20bed%20and%20ended%20up%20shaking%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20certitudes.%20I%20needed%20the%20eminent%20jurist%E2%80%99s%20help%20in%20far%20more%20than%20understanding%20the%20parameters%20of%20%E2%80%98grave%20and%20sudden%20provocation%E2%80%99%20cited%20by%20Commander%20Nanavati%E2%80%99s%20swashbuckling%20lawyers%20and%20dissed%20by%20staid%20judges%20of%20sessions%20and%20high%20court.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20case%20had%20put%20the%20last%20nail%20in%20the%20jury%20system%E2%80%99s%20coffin%3B%20split%20the%20legal%20establishment%20over%20the%20%E2%80%98unusual%20and%20unprecedented%E2%80%99%20favours%20being%20granted%20to%20a%20man%20convicted%20of%20murder%20but%20with%20friends%20in%20high%20places%20(then%20defence%20minister%20Krishna%20Menon%20told%20a%20foreign%20correspondent%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20did%20not%20want%20the%20stain%20of%20turpitude%20to%20sully%20the%20reputation%20of%20a%20promising%20young%20naval%20officer%E2%80%99).%20It%20led%20to%20the%20summoning%20of%20a%20full%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20decide%20on%20how%20the%20Governor%E2%80%99s%20powers%20of%20pardon%20under%20Art%20161%20could%20be%20reconciled%20with%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20mandate%20of%20supremacy%20under%20Art%20142.%20Even%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20was%20drawn%20into%20the%20legal%20maelstrom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffali-nariman-obituary-indira-jaising%5C%22%3EAt%20a%20Time%20When%20the%20Battles%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Future%20Will%20Be%20Fought%20in%20its%20Courts%2C%20We%20Will%20Miss%20Fali%20Nariman%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20as%20I%20settled%20down%20with%20pen%20and%20attention%20poised%2C%20Nariman%20simply%20handed%20me%20a%20fat%20dossier%20he%E2%80%99d%20already%20assembled.%20It%20contained%20copies%20of%20the%20relevant%20judgments%20that%20otherwise%20would%20have%20been%20herculean%20to%20access%2C%20as%20well%20as%20clippings%20on%20the%20Law%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20deliberations%20over%20ending%20the%20jury%20system%20(%E2%80%98taken%20from%20Britain%20and%20transplanted%20on%20the%20soil%20of%20India%E2%80%99).%20The%20exhaustive%20file%20included%20Nariman%E2%80%99s%20speech%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Gymkhana%20on%20the%20then%20high-octane%20in%20the%20Jessica%20Lal%20case%3B%20it%20showed%20how%20despite%20a%20bar-room%20full%20of%20witnesses%2C%20no%20one%20had%20came%20forward%20to%20testify%20against%20the%20politically%20connected%20Manu%20Sharma%20%E2%80%93%20in%20contrast%2C%20no%20one%20had%20been%20in%20Prem%20Ahuja%E2%80%99s%20dressing%20room%20on%20that%20infamous%20late%20afternoon%20of%20April%2027%2C%201959%20except%20the%20dead%20victim%20and%20the%20cuckolded%20husband%20who%E2%80%99d%20gone%20there%20armed%20with%20a%20loaded%20Smith%20and%20Wesson.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20without%20any%20further%20reference%2C%20Nariman%20began%20chatting%20casually%20of%20matters%20unrelated%2C%20with%20that%20moustache-lurking%20smile.%20Of%20Bombay%20Parsi%20politics%2C%20but%20discreetly%20skirting%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20larger%20one.%20With%20quiet%20pride%20in%20his%20son%20Rohinton%20not%20yet%20elevated%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Bench%20and%20his%20daughter%20Anahita%2C%20a%20paediatric%20psychological%20counsellor%3B%20with%20unabashed%20warmth%20of%20his%20grandchildren%20and%20great%20grandchildren.We%20talked%20of%20his%20daughter-in-law%20Sanaya%2C%20whose%20food%20scientist%20father%20shared%20the%20same%20name%20as%20my%20late%20ex-husband%20Jehangir%2C%20and%20her%20elegant%20mother%2C%20also%20a%20Bachi%2C%20with%20whom%20we%20spent%20wonderful%20mornings%20at%20their%20exotic-tree%20filled%20farmhouse%20in%20Golwad%20on%20weekend%20trips%20to%20our%20own%2C%20now-lost%2C%20%3Cem%3Echikoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20orchard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMid-way%20Bapsi%2C%20his%20soul-mate%20and%20cookery-expert%2C%20joined%20us%20bearing%20a%20large%20tin%20of%20the%20Hyderabadi%20version%20of%20Irani-bakery%20%3Cem%3Ekhari%3C%2Fem%3E%20biscuits.%20He%20was%20so%20manifestly%20attached%20to%20her%2C%20so%20caring%20of%20her%20during%20her%20long%20illness%2C%20that%20he%20refused%20my%20invitation%20to%20our%20Mumbai%20TOI%20litfest%2C%20because%20%E2%80%98My%20wife%20is%20too%20ill%2C%20and%20I%20need%20to%20be%20with%20her%E2%80%99.%20Something%20of%20him%20died%20too%20when%20she%20did%20in%202020.%20As%20the%20Parzor%20tribute%20to%20%E2%80%98Fali%20Uncle%E2%80%99%20ended%2C%20%E2%80%98May%20you%20rest%20now%20with%20Bapsi%20Aunty%20in%20Garothan%20Behesht%2C%20and%20continue%20to%20bless%20us%20all.%E2%80%99%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cem%3EBachi%20Karkaria%20is%20a%20veteran%20journalist%2C%20popular%20columnist%20and%20media%20trainer.%20Her%20best-selling%20books%20include%20%3C%2Fem%3EDare%20To%20Dream%3A%20The%20Life%20of%20Rai%20Bahadur%20M.S.%20Oberoi%2C%20In%20Hot%20Blood%3A%20The%20Nanavati%20Case%20That%20Shook%20India%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EMumbai%20Masti%20%3Cem%3Ewith%20designer%20Krsna%20Mehta%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20Mills.%20Molls%20and%20Moolah%2C%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3ECapture%20The%20Dream%3A%20The%20Many%20Lives%20of%20Captain%20C.P.%20Krishnan%20Nair.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708604114000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21155108%2FUntitled-design-2-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Faapro-fali-the-parsi-communitys-pride-and-the-constitutional-authority-with-a-twinkle-in-his-eye%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fali%20Nariman%20always%20had%20time%20for%20good%20causes%2C%20even%20for%20reporters%20looking%20for%20free%20advice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Faapro-fali-the-parsi-communitys-pride-and-the-constitutional-authority-with-a-twinkle-in-his-eye%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%