8376%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22457%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESorath%20Lohar.%20Photo%3A%20Veengas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESindhis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHidayat%20Lohar%20was%20abducted%20in%202017%20by%20Pakistan%20agencies%20and%20released%20in%202019.%20Sorath%20and%20Sasui%20Lohar%2C%20his%20daughters%2C%20both%20became%20prominent%20activists%20at%20around%202014%2C%20while%20they%20were%20in%20university.%20Sasui%2C%20aged%2031%2C%20also%20leads%20the%20Voice%20for%20Missing%20Persons%20of%20Sindh%20or%20VMPS.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20sisters%20spoke%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20narrating%20why%20their%20father%20and%20other%20Sindhis%20are%20being%20killed%20in%20the%20Sindh%20province.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESorath%20added%20that%20her%20father%20was%20abducted%20for%20a%20second%20time%20in%202023%20and%20warned%20to%20stop%20Sorath%20from%20leading%20VMPS.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20had%20been%20inactive%20in%20politics%20since%20his%20release%20and%20was%20suffering%20from%20illness.%20Yet%2C%20he%20loved%20Sindh.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20asked%20why%20it%E2%80%99s%20considered%20a%20crime%20for%20Sindhis%20to%20love%20their%20land%2C%20even%20though%20they%20are%20non-violent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20added%20that%20her%20father%20was%20not%20the%20first%20to%20be%20killed.%20Earlier%2C%20Niaz%20Lashari%20was%20killed%20in%202017%2C%20and%20no%20one%20came%20forward%20to%20help%20his%20family%2C%20the%20sisters%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAsif%20Panhwar%20and%20Munir%20Cholani%20were%20also%20killed.%20Munir%20was%20brutally%20tortured%20after%20abduction%20and%20then%20left%20paralysed.%20What%20happened%20to%20him%3F%20Security%20agencies%20took%20him%20off%20the%20bus%20and%20fired%20at%20his%20head%20in%20front%20of%20his%20family%20members%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sisters%20stressed%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20media%20attention%20to%20Sindhi%20or%20Baloch%20people%E2%80%99s%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20voices%20that%20demand%20rights%20irritate%20the%20state%20because%20those%20who%20know%20they%20are%20wrong%20will%20hardly%20accept%20dissenting%20voices%20from%20people%20who%20are%20sons%20and%20daughters%20of%20the%20soil.%20The%20Pakistani%20state%20acts%20fearfully%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sorath%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sisters%20show%20me%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20room%20and%20his%20collection%20of%20Sindhi%20books.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESit-in%20for%20an%20FIR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lohars%20led%20a%20march%20from%20their%20house%20to%20the%20Nasirabad%20highway%20to%20start%20a%20sit-in%20%3Cspan%3Edemanding%20the%20filing%20of%20an%20FIR.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESasui%20chanted%20slogans%20and%20delivered%20speeches%20at%20every%20stop%2C%20urging%20people%20to%20join%20the%20sit-in.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20she%20spoke%20with%20a%20broken%20voice%2C%20emphasizing%20that%20her%20father%20was%20not%20killed%20in%20a%20personal%20feud%20and%20that%20he%20was%20raising%20his%20voice%20for%20Sindhis%20and%20their%20future%20generations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnderstanding%20that%20heavy%20police%20presence%20prevented%20some%20from%20joining%20the%20protest%2C%20Sasui%20asked%20people%20to%20at%20least%20chant%20a%20slogan%20from%20where%20they%20were.%20Young%20people%2C%20even%20children%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20were%20visibly%20poor%2C%20joined%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20protest%20reached%20the%20Nasirabad%20highway%2C%20the%20police%20outnumbered%20the%20protesters.%20Some%20police%20officers%20even%20attempted%20to%20incite%20the%20protesters%2C%20but%20the%20organisers%20remained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESasui%20asked%20how%20it%20was%20that%20when%20the%20family%20possessed%20evidence%2C%20including%20an%20identity%20card%20left%20at%20the%20crime%20scene%20belonging%20to%20a%20person%20from%20Sargodha%2C%20a%20city%20in%20Punjab%2C%20police%20still%20could%20not%20file%20an%20FIR%20by%20naming%20the%20accused.%20She%20said%20there%20has%20been%20pressure%20to%20accede%20to%20an%20FIR%20against%20unknown%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20police%20officer%20at%20the%20spot%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20cops%20would%20register%20an%20FIR%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ebased%20on%20the%20actual%20position.%E2%80%9D%20When%20asked%20about%20what%20the%20%E2%80%9Cactual%20position%E2%80%9D%20entailed%2C%20he%20could%20not%20provide%20a%20clear%20answer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20Sindhi%20nationalist%20leaders%20or%20activists%20were%20present%20at%20the%20sit-in%20which%20only%20saw%20the%20sisters%2C%20along%20with%20their%20two%20young%20brothers%20and%20a%20few%20political%20workers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20response%20from%20across%20Pakistan%20regarding%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20killing%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20has%20been%20raising%20his%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20voice%20for%20missing%20persons%2C%20Sorath%20responded%20that%20she%20never%20expected%20political%20leadership%2C%20Pakistan-based%20feminists%2C%20or%20even%20parliamentarians%20and%20politicians%20to%20speak%20up%20for%20their%20cause.%20She%20said%20that%20it%20had%20been%20three%20days%2C%20and%20not%20a%20single%20politician%20had%20offered%20condolences.%20However%2C%20Dr.%20Mahrang%20Baloch%2C%20prominent%20activist%2C%20had%20tweeted%20about%20her%20father%20and%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20the%20oppressed%20people%E2%80%99s%20struggle.%20Common%20people%20had%20also%20voiced%20support%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESasui%20was%20determined%20that%20she%20would%20continue%20her%20legal%20battle%20to%20get%20justice%20for%20her%20father%2C%20regardless%20of%20how%20long%20the%20process%20might%20take.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThreats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHidayat%E2%80%99s%20widow%20meanwhile%20requested%20this%20journalist%20to%20convince%20her%20daughters%20to%20remain%20silent%20as%20she%20could%20not%20afford%20another%20brutal%20incident%20in%20retaliation%20for%20their%20activism.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20sacrificed%20his%20life%20for%20Sindh%2C%20it%20is%20an%20honour%20that%20he%20was%20killed%20as%20a%20martyr%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESorath%20shared%20that%20Counter%20Terrorism%20Department%20(CTD)%20held%20a%20conference%20against%20her%2C%20alleging%20that%20she%20was%20receiving%20foreign%20funding%20to%20lead%20VMPS.%20%E2%80%9CSecurity%20agencies%20warned%20my%20father%20to%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20continue%20with%20my%20activism.%20Though%20CTD%20has%20not%20established%20any%20kind%20of%20evidence%20of%20funding%2C%20my%20relatives%20are%20pressuring%20me%20to%20step%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20sisters%20are%20resolute%20that%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20live%20in%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20who%20spoke%20to%20this%20journalist%20refused%20to%20be%20named%20out%20of%20fear%20%E2%80%93%20a%20common%20response%20given%20the%20number%20of%20warnings%20and%20threats%20received%20by%20the%20Lohars%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22171038%2FScreenshot-2024-02-2