pointed%20and%20said%20that%20she%20can%20only%20hope%20for%20international%20human%20rights%20organisations%20and%20UN%20to%20urge%20the%20Pakistani%20state%20to%20end%20extrajudicial%20killings%20in%20Sindh%20and%20Balochistan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20still%20do%20not%20understand%20why%20the%20state%20killed%20my%20father%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sasui.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708602141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22170935%2FScreenshot-2024-02-22-at-5.09.06%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-sindhi-activist-hidayat-lohar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20prominent%20activist%2C%20Hidayat%20Lohar%20was%20gunned%20down%20on%20February%2016%2C%202024%2C%20in%20Nasirabad%2C%20near%20Larkana%20city%2C%20Sindh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A71%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-sindhi-activist-hidayat-lohar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Minnesota%20man%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20slaying%20Los%20Angeles%20woman%20found%20inside%20refrigerator%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708600429000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107915346%2Cimgsize-1520112.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fminnesota-man-arrested-on-suspicion-of-slaying-of-los-angeles-woman-found-inside-refrigerator%2Farticleshow%2F107915248.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107915248.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fminnesota-man-arrested-on-suspicion-of-slaying-of-los-angeles-