s%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhit-squad-is-physically-eliminating-putins-critics-jailed-opponent-vladimir-kara-murza-warns-13078165%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhit-squad-is-physically-eliminating-putins-critics-jailed-opponent-vladimir-kara-murza-warns-13078165%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhit-squad-is-physically-eliminating-putins-critics-jailed-opponent-vladimir-kara-murza-warns-13078165%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Alleges%20Rs%2065%20Crore%20%E2%80%98Looted%E2%80%99%20from%20Its%20Accounts%20by%20Income%20Tax%20Officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22150518%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-22-at-3.04.58-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20party%20on%20Thursday%20(February%2022)%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfinancial%20terrorism%E2%80%9D%20and%20alleged%20that%20Rs%2065%20crore%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Clooted%E2%80%9D%20from%20its%20accounts%20by%20banks%20and%20deposited%20to%20the%20government%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20holding%20this%20press%20conference%20to%20reveal%20the%20so-called%20financial%20terrorism%20imposed%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20on%20the%20Congress%20party.%20As%20per%20the%20latest%20information%20from%20the%20banks%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20forced%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20transfer%20approximately%20Rs%2065.89%20crore%20from%20our%20deposits%20to%20the%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20K.C.%20Venugopal%20said%20while%20alleging%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20is%20%E2%80%9Cstealing%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20launching%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP%2C%20Venugopal%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CBasically%20this%20amount%20is%20from%20the%20AICC%20(All%20India%20Congress%20Committee)%2C%20IYC%20(Indian%20Youth%20Congress)%2C%20and%20NSUI%20(National%20Students%20Union%20of%20India)%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnlike%20the%20BJP%2C%20we%20acquired%20this%20money%20from%20ordinary%20workers%20of%20the%20party.%20%5BThe%5D%20Congress%20party%20had%20extensively%20gone%20for%20crowd%20funding%20and%20collected%20money%20from%20the%20poor%20people%20of%20this%20country.%20IYC%20money%20is%20the%20membership%20fees%20of%20ordinary%20IYC%20workers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenugopal%20underlined%20that%20this%20was%20happening%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20country%20and%20asked%20whether%20the%20BJP%20had%20experienced%20this%20under%20the%20UPA%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20questioned%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20does%20it%20mean%20just%20before%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%3F%20The%20account%20of%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%20has%20been%20hijacked%20by%20the%20BJP%20government.%20We%20are%20all%20law%20abiding%20citizens.%20On%20very%20very%20non-serious%20matters%20they%20are%20taking%20away%20our%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBasically%20they%20are%20stealing%20our%20money%20from%20the%20bank.%20This%20is%20to%20deny%20the%20minimum%20level%20playing%20field%20to%20a%20political%20party%20to%20fight%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20ruled%20this%20country.%20Can%20%5Bthe%5D%20BJP%20point%20to%20any%20such%20experience%20under%20%5Bthe%5D%20Congress%20or%20UPA%20government%3F%20Has%20%5Bthe%5D%20BJP%20given%20income%20tax%20as%20a%20party%3F%20This%20is%20a%20clear%20attack%20on%20democratic%20principles.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20shut%20the%20voice%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20opposition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%20that%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-bank-accounts-frozen-election%5C%22%3Efrozen%20its%20bank%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20demanded%20Rs%20210%20crore%20as%20recovery%20over%20an%20alleged%2045-day%20delay%20in%20filing%20returns%20and%20cash%20contributions%20from%20its%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20later%20announced%20on%20the%20same%20day%20that%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20(ITAT)%20un-froze%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20%E2%80%9Cpending%20further%20hearing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-bank-accounts-frozen-election%5C%22%3EDay%20After%20SC%20Quashes%20Electoral%20Bonds%2C%20Congress%20Says%20Accounts%20Frozen%3B%20Cloud%20Over%20%E2%80%98Interim%20Relief%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20same%20press%20conference%2C%20Congress%20treasurer%20Ajay%20Maken%20said%20that%20while%20the%20hearing%20was%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20yesterday%20(February%2021)%2C%20income%20tax%20officials%20went%20to%20bank%20branches%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2020)%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthreatened%E2%80%9D%20them%20and%20collected%20Rs%2065.8%20crore%20through%20demand%20drafts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20day%20before%20the%20hearing%2C%20Income%20Tax%20officials%20went%20to%20the%20bank%20branches%20and%20threatened%20them%20and%20collected%20Rs%2065.8%20crore%20through%20demand%20draft%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20details%20provided%20by%20the%20party%2C%20a%20total%20amount%20of%20Rs%2065.88%20crore%20was%20collected%20from%20AICC%20accounts%20in%20the%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%2C%20Union%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%20as%20well%20as%20the%20IYC%20account%20and%20NSUI%20accounts%20in%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20turn%20of%20events%20started%20suddenly%20when%2C%20on%20February%2014%2C%20the%20IT%20Department%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20four%20bankers%20of%2011%20branches%20of%20AICC%2C%20Youth%20Congress%20and%20NSUI%20asking%20them%20to%20deposit%20Rs%20135%2C06%2C88%2C984.%20(In%20some%20banks%20the%20demand%20was%20Rs%2075.17%2C97%2C015.73)%2C%20the%20total%20being%20more%20than%20210%20crores)-%20to%20the%20Government.%20Since%20no%20bank%20had%20such%20amounts%20in%20our%20accounts%2C%20our%20accounts%20were%20virtually%20frozen%20and%20thus%20inoperable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%20that%20IT%20officials%20had%20informed%20the%20ITAT%20that%20it%20has%20not%20frozen%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20bank%20accounts%20but%20only%20asked%20for%20a%20lien%20on%20the%20amount%20according%20to%20an%20earlier%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20brazenly%20the%20IT%20department%20went%20a%20step%20ahead%20and%20transferred%20our%20funds%20to%20the%20government%20accounts%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20said%20that%20the%20issue%20pertains%20to%20income%20tax%20returns%20filed%20for%20the%20financial%20year%202019-2018%20on%20February%202%2C%202019%20relevant%20to%20the%20assessment%20year%202018-2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20IT%20department%20found%20fault%20with%20the%20INC%20that%20out%20of%20the%20aggregate%20voluntary%20contributions%20of%20Rs%20142.83%20crores%2C%20Rs%2014.49%20lakhs%20were%20received%20in%20cash%2C%20each%20donation%20being%20more%20than%20Rs%202%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20said%20that%20the%20cash%20contribution%20was%20the%20monthly%20salaries%20given%20by%20MPs%20and%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20give%20our%20accounts%20to%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20by%20December%2031%2C%20but%20we%20gave%20it%20on%20February%202%2C%202019.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20we%20were%20imposed%20a%20penalty%20of%20Rs%20201%20crores.%20This%20has%20never%20happened%20till%20date%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Maken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNext%20is%20the%20question%20of%20timing.%20Now%20after%20five%20years%2C%20the%20government%20and%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20have%20woken%20up%2C%20when%20elections%20are%20around%20the%20corner.%20What%20kind%20of%20justice%20is%20this%3F%20This%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20cripple%20the%20Congress%20party%20financially%20so%20that%20we%20are%20not%20able%20to%20contest%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20claims%20show%20their%20character%20of%20%E2%80%9Cloot%E2%80%9D%3A%20BJP%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20on%20Thursday%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Shehzad%20Poonawalla%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20claims%20shows%20their%20character%20of%20%E2%80%9Cloot%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Evasooli%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(recovery).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20normal%20tax%20rules%20that%20are%20applicable%20%5Bto%5D%20common%20people%20like%20you%20and%20me%2C%20for%20them%20it%20is%20appearing%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98vasooli%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Income%20Tax%20assessment%20under%20which%20it%20was%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20to%20pay%20Rs%20135%20crores%20was%20done%20on%20July%206%2C%202021.%20Today%20%5Bthe%5D%20Congress%20is%20saying%20that%20political%20parties%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20pay%20income%20tax.%20This%20is%20correct%20as%20per%20Section%2013(A)%3B%20political%20parties%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20pay%20tax%20on%20voluntary%20contributions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Poonawalla%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20you%20consider%20the%20provisos%20given%20under%20the%20Section%2C%20there%20are%20some%20conditions%20that%20have%20been%20laid%20down%2C%20including%20returns%20being%20filed%20on%20time%2C%20%5Band%20that%5D%20voluntary%20contributions%20cannot%20be%20over%20Rs%202%2C000.%20So%20there%20is%20no%20blanket%20coverage%20of%20exemption%20on%20all%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20March%2028%2C%202023%2C%20this%20was%20confirmed%20by%20an%20appellate%20commissioner%2C%20on%20which%20%5Bthe%5D%20Congress%20filed%20an%20appeal.%20The%20law%20says%20that%2020%25%20has%20to%20be%20deposited%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20appeal%2C%20which%20means%20they%20had%20to%20deposit%20Rs%2021%20crores.%20The%20appeal%20was%20dismissed%20and%20instead%20of%20Rs%2021%20crores%2C%20the%20Congress%20deposited%20Rs%2078%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20May%202023%2C%20%5Bthe%5D%20Congress%20filed%20another%20appeal%20but%20did%20not%20ask%20for%20a%20stay%20and%20in%20October%202023%2C%20the%20Congress%20deposited%20Rs%201.72%20crore%20of%20the%2021%20crore%20that%20had%20to%20be%20deposited.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonawalla%20said%20that%20the%20Rs%2065%20crore%20that%20the%20Congress%20referred%20to%20%E2%80%9Chas%20not%20been%20encashed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20nobility%20of%20the%20IT%20department%20that%20the%20Rs%2065%20crores%20that%20is%20being%20talked%20about%2C%20the%20demand%20draft%20has%20not%20been%20encashed%20by%20the%20IT%20officials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%5Btax%5D%20assessment%20came%20because%20you%20flouted%20the%20laws.%20They%20filed%20an%20appeal%2C%20which%20was%20rejected%2C%20they%20deposit%20some%20money%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20ask%20for%20a%20stay.%20They%20go%20for%20a%20second%20appeal%20and%20again%20don%E2%80%99t%20ask%20for%20a%20stay%2C%20and%20when%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20is%20followed%2C%20you%20call%20it%20financial%20terrorism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20misdeeds%20done%20under%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20between%202004-2014%20can%20be%20classified%20as%20financial%20terrorism%20as%20has%20been%20shown%20by%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20white%20paper%20recently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708599045000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22150518%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-22-at-3.04.58-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-alleges-rs-65-crore-looted-from-its-accounts-by-income-tax-officials%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20treasurer%20Ajay%20Maken%20said%20income%20tax%20officials%20went%20to%20the%20bank%20branches%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2020)%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthreatened%E2%80%9D%20them%20and%20collected%20Rs%2065.8%20crore%20through%20demand%20draft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-alleges-rs-65-crore-looted-from-its-accounts-by-income-tax-officials%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Myanmar%20Junta%20Activates%20a%2014-Year-Old%20Conscription%20Law%20to%20Try%20and%20Regain%20Territories%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22160941%2FBurmese_Junta_Leaders_-_Vinyl_on_sidewalk.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20as%20the%20Brotherhood%20Alliance%20is%20continuing%20to%20snatch%20newer%20areas%20from%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Junta%2C%20the%20military%20has%20activated%20a%2014-year-old%20conscription%20law%20to%20be%20able%20to%20draft%20civilians%20between%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018%20and%2045%20into%20the%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20news%20reports%2C%20the%20Junta%20has%20issued%20orders%20to%20military-owned%20garment%20factories%20to%20mass-produce%20uniforms.%20The%20order%20came%20just%20days%20after%20the%20Junta%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20on%20February%2010%20to%20activate%20the%20law%20it%20had%20brought%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Military%20Service%20Law%2C%20young%20men%20between%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018-45%20and%20women%20between%2018%20and%2035%20may%20be%20conscripted%20into%20the%20military%20up%20to%20five%20years.%20Those%20who%20evade%20the%20call%20or%20help%20someone%20do%20so%20can%20be%20imprisoned%20for%20up%20to%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irrawaddy.com%2Fnews%2Fburma%2Fmyanmar-junta-launches-mass-production-of-army-uniforms-for-conscription.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Irrawaddy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20call-up%20(to%20civilians)%20will%20begin%20after%20the%20Thingyan%20holiday%20in%20April%20with%20up%20to%205000%20people%20drafted%20in%20each%20intake.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20report%20quoting%20an%20unidentified%20employee%20of%20a%20government-owned%20garment%20factory%20in%20Yangon%20told%20the%20news%20outfit%20that%20the%20unit%20has%20begun%20producing%20uniforms%20from%20February%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20three%20Yangon-based%20units%2C%20the%20order%20has%20been%20received%20by%20military-owned%20factories%20in%20Mandalay%2C%20Bago%20and%20Magwe%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUniform%20for%20militia%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20significant%20is%2C%20these%20factories%20are%20not%20only%20producing%20military%20uniforms%20but%20also%20%E2%80%9Cmilitia%20uniforms%E2%80%9D.%20An%20employee%20from%20one%20of%20the%20three%20Yangon-based%20military-owned%20garment%20factories%20had%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Irrawaddy%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CFabric%20rolls%20arrived%20on%20Feb.%2014%20and%2015%20and%20we%20started%20production%20on%20Feb.%2016.%20We%20are%20making%20two%20types%20of%20garment%20%E2%80%93%20army%20uniforms%20and%20militia%20uniforms.%20We%20have%20to%20make%20over%2010%2C000%20sets%20of%20uniforms.%20They%20are%20likely%20intended%20for%20the%20first%20intake.%E2%80%9D%20The%20news%20report%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20military-owned%20garment%20factory%20in%20Bago%E2%80%99s%20Pyinpongyi%20is%20also%20making%20militia%20and%20military%20uniforms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20defense%20ministry%20has%20instructed%20military-owned%20textile%20and%20garment%20factories%20to%20supply%20over%20100%2C000%20sets%20of%20army%20uniforms%20for%20conscripted%20recruits%20and%20militias%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupport%20in%20Northern%20Shan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20which%20militias%20are%20to%20align%20with%20the%20Junta%20to%20fight%20the%20three%20militias%20that%20form%20part%20of%20the%20Brotherhood%20Alliance%20or%20other%20groups%20within%20the%20country%20resisting%20the%20military%20rule%20with%20arms.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20the%20Pa-O%20National%20Army%20(PNA)%2C%20active%20in%20the%20southern%20Shan%20State%2C%20is%20said%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irrawaddy.com%2Fnews%2Fburma%2Fpa-o-militia-backs-myanmar-junta-conscription-by-forcibly-recruiting-civilians.html%5C%22%3Ealready%20begun%20using%20the%20conscription%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20compulsorily%20draft%20young%20men%20and%20women%20into%20its%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPNA%20controls%20the%20Pa-O%20self-administered%20areas%20comprising%20Hopong%2C%20Hsi%20Hseng%20and%20Panlong%20townships%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20Shan%20State%2C%20located%20close%20to%20Thailand%E2%80%99s%20cities%20like%20Chiang%20Mai%2C%20Chiang%20Rai%2C%20etc.%20After%20signing%20a%20peace%20agreement%20with%20the%20earlier%20military%20regime%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20the%20PNA%2C%20which%20has%20been%20fighting%20for%20self-rule%20since%201949%2C%20has%20begun%20militarily%20protecting%20officially%20the%20three%20townships%20of%20southern%20Shan%20State%20governed%20by%20Pa-O%20National%20Organisation%20(PNO).%20The%20present%20PNA%20leader%20Aung%20Kham%20Hti%20is%20close%20to%20the%20Junta%20chief%20Ming%20Aung%20Hliang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUN%20condemns%20move%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2021%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20Junta%E2%80%99s%20activation%20of%20the%20conscription%20law%2C%20Tom%20Andrews%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%E2%80%99%20special%20rapporteur%20on%20the%20situation%20of%20human%20rights%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20sign%20of%20the%20Junta%E2%80%99s%20weakness%20and%20desperation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndrews%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYoung%20people%20are%20horrified%20by%20the%20possibility%20of%20being%20forced%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20junta%E2%80%99s%20reign%20of%20terror.%20The%20numbers%20fleeing%20across%20borders%20to%20escape%20conscription%20will%20surely%20skyrocket.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20UN%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146802%5C%22%3Enearly%202.7%20million%20people%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Myanmar%20of%20which%20almost%202.4%20million%20were%20after%20the%20February%202021%20takeover%20of%20the%20country%20by%20the%20Junta%20after%20rejecting%20the%20election%20results%20that%20had%20re-elected%20the%20Aung%20San%20Suu%20Kyi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20internal%20displacement%2C%20several%20have%20fled%20to%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20neighbouring%20countries%20too%2C%20including%20some%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20north-eastern%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%20asking%20Myanmar%20to%20resume%20its%20border%20trade%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pro-democracy%20Brotherhood%20Alliance%2C%20formed%20in%20mid-2019%2C%20comprises%20the%20Arakan%20Army%20(AA)%2C%20the%20Myanmar%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(MNDA)%20and%20Taang%20National%20Liberation%20Army%20(TNLA).%20Together%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Operation%201027%20started%20this%20past%20October%2C%20these%20militias%20have%20gained%20control%20of%20a%20large%20swathe%20of%20areas%20key%20to%20the%20China-Myanmar%20border%20trade%20in%20the%20northern%20Shan%20State.%20The%20Brotherhood%20Alliance%20is%20widely%20seen%20to%20have%20China%E2%80%99s%20backing%2C%20with%20China%20brokering%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fmyanmar-rebel-alliance-agree-ceasefire-with-ruling-military-rebel-group-tnla-2024-01-12%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98temporary%E2%80%99%20ceasefire%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20Junta%20and%20Alliance%20forces%20on%20January%2011.%20The%20two%20sides%20met%20at%20China%E2%80%99s%20behest%20in%20the%20Chinese%20city%20Kunming%20for%20two%20days%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Junta-Brotherhood%20Alliance%20fights%20have%20continued%2C%20the%20China-brokered%20ceasefire%20has%20led%20to%20silencing%20of%20guns%20and%20bomb-dropping%20by%20both%20sides%20considerably%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20northern%20Shan%20State%2C%20thus%20creating%20a%20situation%20to%20restore%20Myanmar-China%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2019%2C%20the%20governor%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20Yunnan%20province%20which%20borders%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Kokang%20region%20taken%20over%20by%20Alliance%20forces%2C%20met%20Junta%20chief%20Ming%20Aung%20Hliang%20and%20the%20minister%20for%20commerce%2C%20Htun%20Ohn%2C%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20Naypyitaw%2C%20to%20discuss%20restarting%20the%20trade%20route%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20leader%20had%20asked%20the%20trade%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20in%20their%20local%20currencies.%20According%20to%20the%20Myanmar%20government%E2%80%99s%20data%2C%20the%20border%20trade%20value%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20had%20increased%20substantially%20to%20stand%20at%20%241.82%20billion%20in%20the%202022-23%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMyanmar%20conducts%20border%20trade%20with%20China%20in%20the%20townships%20of%20Muse%2C%20Lweje%2C%20Hinshwehaw%2C%20Kampaiti%2C%20and%20Kengtung.%20The%20Muse%20border%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moi.gov.mm%2Fmoi%3Aeng%2Fnews%2F12476%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMyanmar%2520registered%2520%25241.82%2520billion%2520of%2Cthe%2520trade%2520worth%2520%25241.58%2520billion.%5C%22%3Esaw%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20trade%3C%2Fa%3E%20worth%20%241.58%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20Alliance%20forces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irrawaddy.com%2Fnews%2Fmyanmar-china-watch%2Fgovernor-of-chinas-yunnan-myanmar-junta-boss-discuss-ways-to-resume-border-trade.html%5C%22%3Econtrol%20the%20entire%20belt%3C%2Fa%3E%20except%20Muse.%20Some%20townships%20along%20the%20Muse-Mandalay%20highway%20are%20also%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20militias%20which%20have%20started%20levying%20a%20parallel%20tax%20from%20the%20goods%20trucks%20passing%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20China%20shares%20a%202%2C127-km-long%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20border%20with%20that%20country%20is%201%2C643%20km.%20While%20Chinese%20border%20trade%20with%20Myanmar%20has%20grown%20over%20the%20years%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20border%20trade%20with%20Myanmar%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2023%2F11%2Foperation-1027-is-changing-myanmars-frontier-geographies-is-india-ready%2F%5C%22%3Edismal%201%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20its%20total%20trade%20with%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Look%2FAct%20East%20Policy%20has%20been%20aimed%20at%20expanding%20such%20border%20trade.%20India%20has%2C%20therefore%2C%20been%20pumping%20in%20huge%20investments%20in%20building%20adequate%20infrastructure%20in%20both%20Bangladesh%20and%20Myanmar%2C%20and%20connecting%20them%20particularly%20to%20the%20northeastern%20states%20that%20share%20long%20boundaries%20with%20these%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20recent%20taking%20over%20of%20certain%20border%20townships%20along%20Manipur%20and%20Mizoram%20by%20the%20armed%20militia%20not%20known%20to%20be%20India-friendly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Funderstanding-indias-interests-in-myanmars-paletwa-that-pro-democracy-forces-snatched-from-junta%5C%22%3Emay%20likely%20come%20in%20the%20way%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20India%20expediting%20its%20border%20trade%20with%20Myanmar%20through%20ports%20and%20roads%20it%20has%20constructed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708598450000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22160941%2FBurmese_Junta_Leaders_-_Vinyl_on_sidewalk.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmyanmar-junta-activates-a-14-year-old-conscription-law-to-try-and-regain-territories%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Junta%20has%20also%20issued%20orders%20to%20military-owned%20garment%20factories%20to%20mass-produce%20uniforms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmyanmar-junta-activates-a-14-year-old-conscription-law-to-try-and-regain-territories%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20to%20%E2%80%98Inaugurate%E2%80%99%205%20AIIMS%20Next%20Week%2C%20But%20Are%20They%20'New'%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22160619%2FUntitled-design-2-5.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Union%20health%20minister%20Dr%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%2C%20on%20February%2019%2C%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20inaugurate%20%E2%80%9Ca%20new%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Science%20(AIIMS)%20in%20Jammu.%E2%80%9D%20A%20press%20release%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D2007364%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econfirmed%20that%20the%20PM%20did%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20February%2020.%20Additionally%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported%20quoting%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20said%20that%20the%20PM%20will%20also%20inaugurate%20AIIMS%20in%20Rajkot%2C%20Mangalagiri%2C%20Bathinda%2C%20Raebareli%20and%20Kalyani%20next%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cinauguration%E2%80%9D%20is%20designed%20to%20project%20an%20impression%20of%20a%20new%20AIIMS.%20Inauguration%20sprees%20have%20been%20common%20by%20governments%20before%2C%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20polls%20expected%20to%20be%20announced%20in%20a%20few%20weeks.%20But%20interestingly%2C%20all%20five%20AIIMS%20which%20are%20set%20to%20be%20inaugurated%2C%20are%20not%20new%20and%20have%20been%20functional%2C%20for%20some%20time%20now%2C%20even%20if%20partially.%20Some%2C%20like%20the%20AIIMS%20Mangalagiri%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20has%20been%20functional%20since%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20AIIMS%20Kalyani%E2%80%99s%20official%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faiimskalyani.edu.in%2Faiims-kalyani%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal-based%20institute%20%E2%80%9Cstarted%20its%20first%20academic%20session%20from%20September%2004%2C%202019%2C%20with%20a%20batch%20of%2050%20MBBS%20students.%E2%80%9D%20The%20website%20also%20shows%20that%20the%20hospital%20currently%20has%20as%20many%20as%2039%20functioning%20departments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAIIMS%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Flucknow%2Frae-bareli-aiims-opd-starts-service-5307272%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERaebareli%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20got%20its%20first%20Out%20Patient%20Department%20(OPD)%20in%202018.%20It%20began%20its%20first%20academic%20session%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAIIMS%20Mangalagiri%20became%20operational%20in%202018%20with%20a%20temporary%20campus%20in%20Vijayawada%2C%20but%20then%20started%20operating%20from%20its%20main%20campus%20in%202019.%20The%20official%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aiimsmangalagiri.edu.in%2Finstitution%2Fabout-us%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20AIIMS%20Mangalagiri%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20March%202019%20OPD%20services%20was%20started%20in%20the%20Permanent%20campus%20at%20Mangalagiri%2C%20Guntur.%20Thereafter%20AIIMS%20gradually%20moved%20into%20its%20designated%20campus%20as%20newly%20constructed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAIIMS%20Bhatinda%E2%80%99s%20official%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faiimsbathinda.edu.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20shows%20that%20it%20currently%20has%2039%20functioning%20departments.%20AIIMS%20in%20Rajkot%20also%20began%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faiimsrajkot.edu.in%2Ftt2020%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efirst%20academic%20session%20in%202020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20as%20per%20its%20official%20website.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20all%20these%20five%20AIIMS%20being%20functional%20for%20at%20least%20two%20years%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20set%20to%20inaugurate%20these%20institutes%20under%20%E2%80%98Ayushman%20Bharat%2C%20Viksit%20Bharat%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuddy%20AIIMS%20picture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fpm-modi-aiims-functioning%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20Banjot%20Kaur%20has%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20earlier%20on%20the%20state%20of%20partially%20functional%20AIIMS%20being%20earlier%20declared%20as%20having%20been%20completed.%20But%20the%20truth%20conceals%20a%20situation%20where%2C%20at%20least%20till%20last%20year%2C%20nine%20years%20after%20the%20Modi%20government%20took%20office%2C%20and%2022%20AIIMS%20(as%20opposed%20to%207%20earlier)%20decreed%20as%20being%20set%20up%2C%20none%20were%20fully%20functional.%20According%20to%20the%20reply%20given%20by%20health%20minister%20Mandaviya%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20February%203%2C%202023%2C%20the%2016%20AIIMS-like%20institutions%20are%20under%20%E2%80%98various%20stages%20of%20operationalisation%E2%80%99%20and%20only%20limited%20OPD%20and%20in-patient%20department%20(IPD)%20services%20are%20available.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20these%2016%20AIIMS-like%20institutions%20were%20announced%20in%202014%20itself%2C%20for%20example%2C%20AIIMS%20Gorakhpur%20(Uttar%20Pradesh)%2C%20AIIMS%20Mangalagiri%20(Andhra%20Pradesh)%2C%20AIIMS%20Nagpur%20(Maharashtra)%20and%20AIIMS%20Kalyani%20(West%20Bengal).%20Yet%2C%20all%20of%20these%20institutions%20are%20offering%20only%20limited%20OPD%20and%20IPD%20services%20and%20do%20not%20figure%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98fully%20functional%E2%80%99%20list.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMultiple%20%E2%80%98inaugurations%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20simple%20Google%20search%20shows%20how%20all%20of%20these%20AIIMS%20now%20being%20inaugurated%2C%20have%20had%20inauguration%20ceremonies%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20then%20Union%20health%20ministers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20one%20PIB%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1597213%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reports%20about%20Dr.%20Harsh%20Vardhan%2C%20the%20then%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Family%20Welfare%20inaugurating%2011%20OPD%20centres%20at%20AIIMS%20Bhatinda.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22152206%2FScreenshot-2024-02-22-at-3.21.45%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x509.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%