E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20he%20undertook%20the%20challenge%20of%20transforming%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20dilapidated%20school%20he%20was%20assigned%20to%20teach%20in%202018%2C%20he%20did%20so%20with%20unwavering%20determination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20risk%20of%20sounding%20too%20unrealistic%2C%20I%20want%20to%20emphasise%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20renovating%20the%20school%2C%20I%20had%20nothing%20but%20a%20passion%20towards%20education.%20The%20school%20had%20under%2023%20students%20back%20then%2C%20and%20today%2C%20we%20have%20more%20than%20100%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gopal%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20students%20at%20the%20Integrated%20Middle%20School%20in%20Mohanpura%20Colony%20was%20made%20possible%20after%20Gopal%20took%20on%20the%20mission%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F285414%2Fgerman-teacher-starts-ngo-renovate-kerala-anganwadis-helps-bring-girls-to-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenovating%20the%20school.%20%3C%2Fa%3ETowards%20this%2C%20he%20spent%20Rs%203%20lakh%20from%20his%20own%20pocket%2C%20using%20which%20he%20revamped%20the%20walls%20and%20washrooms%2C%20planted%20a%20garden%2C%20brought%20water%20to%20the%20school%2C%20and%20set%20up%20a%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20a%20neglected%20school%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Gopal%20was%20assigned%20to%20the%20middle%20school%2C%20what%20greeted%20him%20were%20a%20handful%20of%20students%20and%20four%20poorly%20lit%20classrooms%20masquerading%20as%20a%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20school%20was%20in%20a%20deplorable%20state%2C%20to%20put%20it%20mildly.%20The%20walls%20lacked%20paint%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20noticeable%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20in%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20eyes%2C%20which%20troubled%20me%20the%20most.%20However%2C