every%20second%20child%20was%20malnourished%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20one%20of%20his%20visits%20to%20an%20%3Cem%3Eanganwadi%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecentre%20when%20IAS%20Avi%20Prasad%20saw%20a%20year-old%20Sakshi%20lying%20in%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20arms.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20looked%20very%20weak.%20After%20inquiring%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20that%20her%20father%20was%20unemployed%20and%20they%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20look%20after%20her%20nutritional%20requirements.%20She%20also%20developed%20a%20heart%20disease%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20a%20proper%20diet%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20sought%20help%20from%20the%20community%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20industrialists%20wished%20to%20adopt%20that%20child.%20With%20his%20support%2C%20Sakshi%20underwent%20a%20hernia%20operation%20and%20was%20also%20provided%20with%20additional%20nutrition%20via%20a%20special%20nutrition%20kit.%20Because%20of%20the%20timely%20intervention%2C%20she%20is%20a%20healthy%20and%20nourished%20child%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20when%20I%20thought%20of%20replicating%20this%20approach%20to%20help%20other%20children%20in%20similar%20situations%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-2-1708432198.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Avi%20points%20out%20that%20the%20economic%20burden%20was%20the%20major%20factor%20behind%20the%20malnutrition%20crisis%20in%20the%20district.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-2-1708432198.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-2-1708432198-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-2-1708432198-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-2-1708432198-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-2-1708432198-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342451%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAvi%20points%20out%20that%20the%20economic%20burden%20was%20the%20major%20factor%20behind%20the%20malnutrition%20crisis%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20nearly%20half%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%2Fnfhs%2FNFHS-5_FCTS%2FMP%2FKatni.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E49.5%20percent%3C%2Fa%3E)%20of%20under-five%20children%20in%20Katni%20suffered%20from%20stunting%20(below-average%20height%20for%20their%20age)%2C%20with%2044%20percent%20of%20these%20children%20also%20being%20underweight%20(weighing%20below%20the%20healthy%20range%20for%20their%20age).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvi%20points%20out%20that%20the%20economic%20burden%20was%20the%20major%20factor%20behind%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338306%2Fias-officer-shubham-gupta-used-artificial-intelligence-to-fight-malnutrition-govt-schools-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emalnutrition%20crisis%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20district.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20impoverished%20families%20are%20unable%20to%20afford%20a%20nutritious%20diet%20for%20their%20children.%20Although%20the%20Government%20allocates%20additional%20take-home%20rations%20that%20comprise%20wheat%2C%20rice%2C%20or%20grams%20for%20every%20malnourished%20family%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20extra%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Avi%2C%20who%20joined%20Katni%20as%20a%20collector%20in%20Nove