%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20Hygenco%20to%20understand%20the%20need%20for%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20how%20it%20will%20ensure%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20India%20needs%20green%20hydrogen%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20pursuing%20engineering%20in%202005%2C%20Amit%20completed%20his%20higher%20studies%20in%20business%20administration%20at%20Shailesh%20J%20Mehta%20School%20of%20Management%2C%20IIT-Bombay%20in%202010.%20He%20commenced%20his%20career%20as%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Vivaan%20Solar%2C%20a%20leading%20solar%20plant%20installation%20company%20offering%20turnkey%20solar%20power%20plants%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hygenco%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20construct%20and%20operate%20a%20100%20percent%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20Maharashtra.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-3-1707917516-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341882%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHygenco%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20construct%20and%20operate%20a%20100%20percent%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20Maharashtra.%